the%20winter%202022%20issue%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmagazinec.com%2Fculture%2Fso-good-at-playing-bad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EC%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20said%20they%20shared%20a%20one-bedroom%20hotel%20room%20for%20almost%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20mom%2C%20my%20dad%2C%20my%20brother%2C%20and%20I%20were%20in%20a%20regular%20one-bedroom%20hotel%20room%20for%20nine%20months.%26quot%3B%20Sweeney%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20was%2016%20%E2%80%94%20not%20the%20year%20when%20you%20want%20to%20be%20living%20in%20a%20hotel%2C%20sharing%20a%20bed%20with%20your%20mom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20she%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.womenshealthmag.com%2Flife%2Fa45791583%2Fsydney-sweeney-cover-story-interview%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWomen's%20Health%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20move%20was%20financially%20crippling%20for%20the%20family%2C%20and%20they%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20keep%20their%20house%20in%20Spokane%2C%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20watched%20my%20parents%20lose%20a%20lot.%20We%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%2C%20and%20they%20lost%20their%20house%20back%20home%20on%20the%20lake.%20We%20couldn't%20afford%20life%20in%20L.A.%20We%20couldn't%20afford%20life%20anywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESydney's%20parents%20divorced%20shortly%20before%20she%20landed%20%26quot%3BEuphoria%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sydney%20Sweeney%20as%20Cassie%20Howard%20on%20season%20two%20of%20%26quot%3BEuphoria.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62015a68fa4f1f0018264af3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221273%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESydney%20Sweeney%20as%20Cassie%20Howard%20on%20season%20two%20of%20%26quot%3BEuphoria.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EEddy%20Chen%2FHBO%20Max%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESydney's%20career%20started%20to%20take%20off%20in%202018%20w