0structure%20of%20judiciary%20in%20the%20country%2C%20then%20you%20were%20certainly%20wrong.%20The%20edifice%20of%20the%20Indian%20judiciary%20has%20other%20bastions%20of%20partisanship%2C%20always%20waiting%20to%20go%20one%20step%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20were%20still%20consuming%20the%20shift%20by%20former%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20judge%20Ganguly%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20another%20judge%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20proved%20that%20renunciation%20of%20office%20was%20not%20the%20%3Cem%3Esine%20qua%20non%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20a%20judge%20to%20prove%20their%20political%20loyalty.%20The%20same%20allegiance%20could%20be%20pledged%20while%20one%20was%20in%20office%2C%20Additional%20Sessions%20Judge%20Ravi%20Kumar%20Diwakar%20demonstrated%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fex-gyanvapi-case-judge-hails-philosopher-king-adityanath-in-order-indicting-muslim-cleric%5C%22%3Eorder%20he%20passed%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20regards%20to%20a%20riot%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Bareilly%2C%20following%20a%20dispute%20over%20the%20shift%20of%20route%20of%20a%20group%20of%20Muslims%20heading%20to%20join%20a%20larger%20procession%2C%20in%20March%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20order%2C%20Judge%20Diwakar%20declared%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20Raza%20Khan%20as%20the%20main%20conspirator%20and%20mastermind%20of%20what%20he%20called%20the%202010%20riots%20of%20Bareilly%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20summoning%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20to%20the%20court.%20Based%20on%20witness%20reports%2C%20Judge%20Diwakar%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20since%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20holds%20the%20status%20of%20the%20leader%20of%20a%20religious%20family%20and%20is%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Ittehad-e-Millat%20Council%20(IMC)%2C%20he%20has%20great%20influence%20over%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20The%20judge%20further%20asserted%20that%20Plato%2C%20in%20his%20book%20%3Cem%3ERepublic%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20illustrates%20a%20religious%20person%20on%20the%20seat%20of%20authority%20as%20capable%20of%20achieving%20positive%20results.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20word%20justice%20was%20a%20reference%20to%20religion%20in%20Plato%E2%80%99s%20age%2C%20and%20that%20Plato%20argued%20for%20a%20religious%20person%20at%20the%20position%20of%20power%20for%20their%20quality%20of%20leading%20a%20life%20of%20sacrifice%20and%20dedication%20instead%20of%20gratification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20much%20opinionated%20speech%20of%20the%20judge%20delivered%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20judicial%20order%20is%20followed%20by%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20an%20ode%20to%20today%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98philosopher%20king%E2%80%99.%20Without%20any%20mincing%20of%20words%2C%20Judge%20Diwakar%E2%80%99s%20oratory%20took%20a%20turn%20towards%20the%20present%20and%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20in%20the%20present%20time%2C%20Mahant%20Baba%20Shri%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20ji%20of%20the%20Siddhapeeth%20Gorakhnath%20Temple%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20current%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20has%20proved%20Plato%E2%80%99s%20concept%20to%20be%20true.%E2%80%9D%20He%20added%20that%20a%20religious%20person%20doing%20the%20opposite%2C%20or%20inciting%20their%20community%2C%20ultimately%20leads%20to%20riots%2C%20of%20which%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20is%20an%20exemplar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20Plato%20might%20have%20wanted%20for%20a%20king%20to%20be%2C%20he%20would%20certainly%20be%20appalled%20to%20find%20a%20judge%20using%20him%20to%20show%20his%20allegiance%20to%20the%20ruler.%20This%20one%20sentence%20should%20be%20sufficient%20for%20the%20higher%20authorities%20in%20the%20judiciary%20to%20take%20away%20his%20judicial%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22New%20India%20and%20The%20Reign%20of%20Bigidiocy%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnew-india-and-the-reign-of-bigidiocy%5C%22%3ENew%20India%20and%20The%20Reign%20of%20Bigidiocy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20gives%20us%20some%20solace%20that%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fallahabad-hc-expunges-bareilly-judges-remarks-hailing-adityanath-blaming-muslims-for-riots%5C%22%3Eexpunged%20the%20personal%20remarks%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Judge%20Diwakar.%20But%20does%20it%20not%20taint%20the%20whole%20order%20itself%3F%20The%20bias%20demonstrated%20in%20the%20statement%20of%20the%20judge%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20order.%20Would%20it%20not%20be%20fair%20that%20the%20order%20is%20put%20in%20abeyance%20and%20a%20different%20judge%20is%20asked%20to%20look%20into%20the%20matter%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%E2%80%99s%20utterances%20praising%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20should%20not%20surprise%20us.%20After%20all%2C%20he%20happens%20to%20be%20the%20same%20judge%20who%20gave%20the%20verdict%20on%20the%20wazukhana%20case%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%2C%20while%20serving%20as%20the%20civil%20judge%20senior%20division%20in%20Varanasi.%20It%20was%20Diwakar%20who%20in%202022%20ordered%20to%20seal%20the%20ablution%20pond%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20complex%20after%20the%20lawyers%20of%20the%20Hindu%20litigants%20claimed%20that%20a%20%E2%80%98shivling%E2%80%99%20was%20found%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20Diwakar%20who%20did%20not%20resist%20videography%20inside%20the%20mosque%20by%20an%20advocate%20commissioner%20appointed%20by%20the%20court%2C%20following%20the%20claim%20that%20there%20was%20a%20deity%20located%20just%20outside%20the%20western%20wall%20of%20Gyanvapi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20of%20the%20judge%20is%20a%20communal%20document%20and%20a%20dogwhistle%20to%20instigate%20suspicion%20and%20hatred%20against%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20not%20merely%20demonstrate%20his%20fidelity%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98philosopher%20king%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20also%20used%20his%20order%20to%20promote%20the%20communal%20politics%20of%20the%20king%20he%20swears%20by.%20He%20wrote%20that%20he%20was%20threatened%20by%20Muslims%20after%20his%20Gyanvapi%20judgement.%20In%20the%20order%20passed%20by%20him%20on%20March%205%2C%20he%20mentioned%20being%20sent%20a%2032-page%20threat%20from%20a%20Muslim%20organisation.%20Even%20after%20filing%20an%20FIR%2C%20there%20have%20not%20been%20any%20arrests%2C%20Diwakar%20stated%20in%20the%20order.%20Despite%20a%20focus%20on%20the%20objective%20details%20of%20his%20subsequent%20account%2C%20Judge%20Diwakar%20did%20not%20forget%20to%20add%20in%20a%20personal%20touch%20to%20the%20order.%20In%20an%20effort%20to%20exhibit%20fervent%20sentiments%2C%20he%20made%20sure%20to%20state%20that%20his%20mother%2C%20his%20younger%20brother%20and%20his%20children%20were%20constantly%20anxious%20about%20his%20safety%20following%20the%20issuance%20of%20the%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Diwakar%20went%20on%20to%20add%20that%20his%20children%20asked%20whether%20what%20the%20news%20channels%20were%20reporting%20about%20their%20father%E2%80%99s%20possible%20attack%20was%20true.%20He%20further%20said%20that%20even%20though%20he%20tries%20to%20allay%20their%20fears%2C%20they%20tell%20their%20father%20that%20they%20are%20not%20na%C3%AFve%2C%20and%20their%20schoolmates%20have%20told%20them%20the%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20can%20understand%20why%20the%20judge%20is%20linking%20his%20Gyanvapi%20order%20and%20its%20fallout%20and%20the%20case%20of%20Maulana%20Tauqeer.%20The%20order%20reads%20like%20a%20public%20statement%20where%20he%20is%20addressing%20his%20chosen%20audience.%20He%20went%20further%20to%20mention%20that%20the%20alleged%20conspirator%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20had%20in%20the%20past%20made%20remarks%20about%20the%20prime%20minister.%20Thereafter%2C%20he%20mentioned%20his%20wife%2C%20the%20only%20family%20member%20left%20to%20be%20cited%2C%20and%20quoted%20her%20to%20suggest%20a%20peculiar%20analogy%20to%20hint%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20as%20capable%20of%20doing%20worse%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Diwakar%20accused%20the%20then%20law%20and%20order%20authorities%20of%20not%20doing%20enough%20to%20keep%20check%20on%20rioters.%20He%20added%20that%20Bareilly%E2%80%99s%20Divisional%20Commissioner%2C%20Senior%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Deputy%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Police%20and%20District%20Magistrate%20allegedly%20supported%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20and%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20work%20according%20to%20the%20say-so%20of%20the%20government%2C%20failed%20to%20act%20legally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20if%20that%20was%20not%20enough%2C%20he%20further%20instructed%20that%20a%20copy%20of%20his%20order%20be%20submitted%20to%20Adityanath%20so%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20may%20take%20action%20against%20police%20officials%20who%20failed%20to%20act%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%20and%20allegedly%20assisted%20Maualana%20Tauqeer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20one%20intently%20reads%20the%20passed%20order%2C%20a%20number%20of%20interesting%20findings%20appear%20before%20the%20eye.%20The%20order%20mentions%20eight%20witnesses%20of%20the%202010%20riot%20in%20Bareilly.%20Witness%20P.W.-3%20clearly%20mentions%20in%20his%20statement%20that%20%E2%80%9Crumours%20spread%20that%20Tauqeer%20Raza%20Khan%20incited%20a%20riot%E2%80%9D.%20We%20find%20the%20judge%20drawing%20the%20conclusion%20that%20the%20witness%E2%80%99s%20statement%20proves%20that%20the%20riot%20sprouted%20after%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%E2%80%99s%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitness%20P.W.-4%2C%20a%20chowki%20in-charge%2C%20states%20that%20because%20of%20his%20duty%2C%20he%20could%20not%20listen%20to%20the%20complete%20speech%20and%20that%20he%20does%20not%20remember%20it%2C%20but%20the%20riot%20erupted%20just%20afterwards.%20Judge%20Diwakar%20concludes%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cclear%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20witness%E2%80%99s%20statement%20that%20the%20riot%20took%20place%20right%20after%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%E2%80%99s%20oratory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20witnesses%2C%20a%20constable%20posted%20near%20the%20site%20where%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20delivered%20his%20speech%20that%20day%2C%20and%20another%20commoner%2C%20present%20their%20versions%20of%20the%20statement.%20Both%20of%20them%20mention%20in%20their%20articulations%20that%20they%20could%20not%20comprehend%20the%20%E2%80%98hard%E2%80%99%20Urdu%20in%20the%20speech.%20However%2C%20they%20claim%20to%20get%20an%20idea%20of%20what%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20pronounced.%20It%20is%20also%20interesting%20to%20note%20that%20the%20constable%20mentions%20a%20unique%20phrase%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Csacrificing%20life%20in%20the%20process%20of%20leading%20the%20procession%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20while%20quoting%20Tauqeer%20Raza%2C%20which%20is%20absent%20from%20all%20other%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20out%20of%20the%20eight%20witnesses%20quoted%20in%20the%20order%20mention%20the%20incident%20of%20protest%20or%20opposition%20from%20the%20Hindu%20faction%2C%20following%20the%20change%20of%20route%20of%20a%20group%20of%20Muslims%20heading%20to%20join%20a%20procession%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20subsequent%20stone-pelting%20(or%20tension)%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%20All%20six%20of%20these%20statements%20say%20that%20these%20occurrences%20precede%20(or%20otherwise%20coincide%20with)%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20Raza%E2%80%99s%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20issuance%20of%20the%20judgment%2C%20Diwakar%20has%20only%20demonstrated%20his%20proclivity%20for%20perpetuating%20bias%20in%20the%20case%20with%20his%20orders.%20Following%20the%20failure%20to%20serve%20summons%20to%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20by%20the%20designated%20police%20station%20in-charge%2C%20Judge%20Diwakar%20directed%20the%20Senior%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Bareilly%2C%20to%20take%20punitive%20actions%20against%20him%20for%20not%20following%20the%20correct%20procedure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20Diwakar%20issued%20a%20non-bailable%20warrant%20against%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20and%20directed%20commanding%20officer%20Pratham%20Sandeep%20Singh%20to%20arrest%20and%20present%20him%20in%20the%20court%20on%20March%2013.%20The%20commanding%20officer%E2%80%99s%20inability%20to%20submit%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20on%20the%20said%20date%20prompted%20Judge%20Diwakar%20to%20instruct%20SSP%20Bareilly%20to%20arrest%20and%20present%20Tauqeer%20Raza%20in%20court%20on%20March%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22What%20a%20College%20Skit%20Says%20About%20the%20Idea%20of%20the%20University%20in%20Assam%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhat-a-college-skit-says-about-the-idea-of-the-university-in-assam%5C%22%3EWhat%20a%20College%20Skit%20Says%20About%20the%20Idea%20of%20the%20University%20in%20Assam%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3Cins%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20All-India%20Lawyers%E2%80%99%20Association%20for%20Justice%20(AILAJ)%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Flawyers-body-urges-cji-to-take-action-against-up-judge-for-making-communal-remarks-in-judgment%5C%22%3Ewritten%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20asking%20for%20Diwakar%E2%80%99s%20observations%20to%20be%20expunged%20from%20the%20record%20(as%20they%20now%20have%20been%2C%20on%20orders%20from%20the%20high%20court)%2C%20and%20has%20described%20his%20conclusions%20as%20perpetuating%20misplaced%20stereotypes%20and%20bigoted%20impressions%20about%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20AILAJ%20has%20also%20opposed%20the%20judge%E2%80%99s%20directive%20that%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20verdict%20be%20delivered%20to%20Adityanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20an%20accused%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%20filed%20a%20transfer%20application%20with%20the%20District%20Judge%20Bareilly%20citing%20Diwakar%E2%80%99s%20clear%20bias%20against%20his%20community%20in%20the%20March%205%20judgment.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20an%20argument%20in%20the%20District%20Court%20on%20March%2018%2C%20where%20the%20date%20for%20the%20issuance%20of%20order%20was%20scheduled%20as%20March%2021%2C%20while%20the%20next%20date%20of%20appearance%20of%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20was%20March%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20write%20these%20lines%2C%20we%20hear%20that%20a%20notice%20has%20been%20affixed%20on%20the%20door%20of%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20while%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20what%20unfolds%20in%20the%20courts%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bias%20in%20the%20police%20against%20Muslims%20is%20well%20documented%20and%20commented%20upon.%20It%20is%20alarming%20to%20see%20the%20same%20bias%20now%20entering%20the%20judiciary.%20Now%20we%20understand%20why%20Judge%20Diwakar%20ordered%20the%20sealing%20of%20the%20wazukhana%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque.%20It%20is%20his%20anti-Muslim%20bias%20which%20drives%20his%20judgement.%20How%20can%20such%20a%20man%20be%20entrusted%20with%20the%20job%20of%20doing%20justice%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20seen%20with%20dismay%20a%20tendency%20in%20the%20judiciary%2C%20right%20from%20the%20trial%20to%20the%20highest%20level%2C%20to%20treat%20Muslims%20with%20suspicion.%20Should%20we%20conclude%20that%20the%20Hindu%20common%20sense%20which%20treats%20Muslims%20as%20conspiratorial%2C%20bigoted%2C%20dangerous%20or%20violent%20is%20also%20the%20judicial%20common%20sense%2C%20at%20least%20at%20the%20primary%20level%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20such%20thoughts%20assail%20us%2C%20we%20see%20reassuring%20orders%20by%20the%20courts%2C%20one%20from%20a%20court%20of%20a%20first%20class%20magistrate%20Devander%20Sharma%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2F6-years-after-17-muslim-men-were-accused-of-celebrating-pakistani-cricket-victory-mp-courts-find-police-case-to-be-false-65fa4ed58daa7%5C%22%3Eacquitting%2016%20Muslim%20men%3C%2Fa%3E%20(one%20died%20in%202019)%20%C2%A0in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20who%20suffered%20prison%20and%20alleged%20torture%20for%20the%20alleged%20crime%20of%20raising%20the%20slogans%20to%20hail%20Pakistan%20and%20celebrating%20the%20victory%20of%20Pakistan%20in%20a%20cricket%20match.%20But%20it%20could%20happen%20only%20after%20the%20Hindu%20complainant%20and%20government%20witnesses%20told%20the%20court%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20make%20false%20allegations%20against%20them.%20What%20would%20happen%20if%20the%20Hindu%20witnesses%20failed%20to%20be%20so%20brave%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20we%20understand%20after%20we%20read%20the%20the%20judgment%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20%3Cem%3EJaved%20Ahmad%20Hajam%20vs%20State%20of%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Hajam%2C%20a%20professor%20in%20a%20college%20in%20Kolhapur%2C%20had%20a%20first%20information%20report%20filed%20against%20him%20for%20promoting%20religious%20disharmony.%20How%20did%20he%20do%20it%3F%20According%20to%20the%20police%2C%20his%20three%20status%20updates%20on%20WhatsApp%20had%20the%20potential%20of%20causing%20violence%20in%20which%20he%20wished%20Pakistan%20and%20Pakistanis%20a%20happy%20Independence%20Day%2C%20commemorated%20August%205%2C%20the%20day%20Article%20370%20was%20diluted%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9CBlack%20Day%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20expressed%20his%20unhappiness%20with%20the%20decision.%20The%20high%20court%20found%20his%20posts%20on%20Kashmir%20objectionable%20and%20refused%20to%20quash%20the%20police%20proceedings%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20fortunately%2C%20came%20to%20his%20aid.%20A%20two-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20quashed%20the%20charges%20against%20Hajam.%20Going%20further%2C%20it%20said%20that%20Hajam%20had%20a%20right%20to%20air%20his%20opinion.%20It%20can%20be%20a%20disagreement%20with%20the%20state%20action%20of%20abrogation%C2%A0%20of%20Article%20370.%20He%20also%20has%20a%20right%20to%20greet%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20two%20cases%20of%20justice%20again%20take%20us%20to%20the%20order%20of%20Judge%20Diwakar%20and%20his%20averment%20in%20his%20order%20which%20is%20clearly%20Islamophobic.%20It%20is%20a%20fit%20case%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20take%20note%20of%20and%20do%20a%20course%20correction%20by%20quashing%20it%20and%20also%20sending%20the%20judge%20for%20constitutional%20sensitisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711025304000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13145914%2FFYj9tb5UIAEsBYD.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fa-judgment-looking-to-reserve-a-future-rajya-sabha-seat%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Judge%20Diwakar's%20comments%20on%20Adityanath%20and%20the%20Muslim%20community%20proved%20that%20renunciation%20of%20office%20is%20not%20a%20prerequisite%20for%20judges%20to%20prove%20their%20political%20loyalty.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fa-judgment-looking-to-reserve-a-future-rajya-sabha-seat%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lok%20Sabha%20elections%3A%20BJP%20releases%20list%20of%209%20candidates%20for%20TN%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711025294000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108682303%2Cimgsize-1013924.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Flok-sabha-elections-bjp-releases-list-of-9-candidates-for-tamil-nadu%2Farticleshow%2F108682255.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Flok-sabha-elections-bjp-releases-list-of-9-candidates-for-tamil-nadu%2Farticleshow%2F108682255.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20write%20an%20advice%20column%20about%20relationships%20and%20money%20%E2%80%94the%20questions%20I%20get%20from%20parents%20apply%20to%20almost%20all%20of%20us%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20