ws%2Ffarah-khan-and-ananya-pandays-fun-reel-will-leave-you-in-splits%2Farticleshow%2F108681787.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108681787.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20director%20and%20choreographer%20Farah%20Khan's%20Instagram%20feed%20is%20full%20of%20hilarious%20videos%20with%20Bollywood%20stars%20that%20she%20often%20shoots%20while%20working%20with%20them.%20Her%20recent%20collaborative%20video%20with%20Ananya%20Panday%20on%20Instagram%20is%20guaranteed%20to%20bring%20laughter%20and%20appreciation%20for%20her%20sense%20of%20humor.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mammootty-Starrer%20%E2%80%98Bramayugam'%20Is%20a%20Folk%20Horror%20Parable%20on%20the%20Rigged%20Status-Quo%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21172813%2FScreenshot-2024-03-21-at-5.27.09-PM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20almost%20always%20damp%20in%20the%20forests%20of%20South%20Malabar%2C%20where%20Rahul%20Sadasivan%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBramayugam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20takes%20place.%20Set%20in%20the%20late%2017th%20century%2C%20when%20the%20Portuguese%20have%20begun%20enslaving%20locals%2C%20one%20can%20see%20beads%20of%20sweat%20on%20Thevan%E2%80%99s%20(Arjun%20Ashokan)%20forehead%20and%20torso%20in%20nearly%20every%20scene.%20The%20air%20feels%20heavy%2C%20warm%20and%20full%20of%20dread.%20After%20escaping%20slavery%2C%20Thevan%20and%20his%20friend%20Koran%20seek%20refuge%20in%20the%20forests.%20The%20wilderness%20alone%20would%20be%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20here%2C%20but%20the%20supernatural%20resides%20in%20plain%20sight%20in%20a%20Rahul%20Sadasivan%20film%20(he%20made%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBhoothakalam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202022).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20very%20first%20night%2C%20Koram%20is%20seduced%20(and%20it%E2%80%99s%20implied%2C%20killed)%20by%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eyakshini%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20female%20spirit.%20Left%20to%20fend%20for%20himself%20in%20the%20forest%20and%20unable%20to%20cross%20the%20strong%20current%20of%20a%20river%2C%20a%20famished%20Thevan%20enters%20a%20severely%20dilapidated%20palace%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20forest.%20Weeds%20encroach%20almost%20all%20parts%20of%20the%20palace%2C%20making%20it%20seem%20like%20it%E2%80%99s%20abandoned.%20When%20Thevan%20enters%20it%20in%20search%20of%20some%20food.%20He%E2%80%99s%20reprimanded%20by%20a%20man%20from%20a%20distance%2C%20when%20he%20picks%20up%20a%20coconut.%20The%20man%20(Sidharth%20Bharathan)%20is%20the%20cook%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20two%20occupants%20in%20the%20palace.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20person%20inhabiting%20the%20palace%20is%20someone%20who%20comes%20from%20a%20lineage%20of%20sorcerers%2C%20Koduman%20Potti%20(Mammootty).%20When%20Thevan%20tells%20Koduman%20that%20he%20used%20to%20sing%20in%20the%20court%20of%20the%20king%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20asked%20to%20sing.%20Impressed%20with%20his%20abilities%20as%20a%20singer%2C%20Koduman%20invites%20Thevan%20to%20be%20his%20guest%20for%20the%20evening.%20Taken%20aback%20by%20his%20abrupt%20kindness%2C%20Thevan%20can%E2%80%99t%20stop%20singing%20Koduman%E2%80%99s%20praises%20at%20first.%20But%20he%20soon%20finds%20out%20that%20anyone%20who%20enters%20the%20palace%2C%20never%20really%20leaves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21172952%2FScreenshot-2024-03-21-at-5.27.31-PM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21172952%2FScreenshot-2024-03-21-at-5.27.31-PM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21172952%2FScreenshot-2024-03-21-at-5.27.31-PM-300x134.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21172952%2FScreenshot-2024-03-21-at-5.27.31-PM-1024x458.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-702684%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22537%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EStill%20from%20Bramayugam.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20from%20video%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBramayugam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20an%20expansively%20constructed%20folk-horror%20parable%20about%20the%20severely-rigged%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Estatus%20quo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20our%20society.%20Where%20Brahmins%20control%20resources%2C%20knowledge%2C%20wealth%20and%20access%20to%20everything%20while%20spouting%20things%20like%20how%20%E2%80%98one%20can%20only%20attain%20this%20privilege%20with%20their%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekarma%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(deeds)%E2%80%99.%20The%20rich%20appear%20to%20play%20%E2%80%98fair%E2%80%99%20with%20those%20with%20fewer%20means.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESadasivan%20visualises%20this%20through%20a%20creepy%20game%20of%20dice%20between%20Kodumon%20and%20Thevan.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20game%20of%20luck%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thevan%20tells%20Kodumon%2C%20who%20is%20visibly%20offended%20by%20the%20statement.%20So%20Kodumon%20invites%20Thevan%20to%20a%20game%2C%20saying%20if%20he%20wins%20he%20can%20leave%20the%20palace.%20But%20if%20he%20loses%2C%20he%20will%20forget%20about%20his%20mother%20and%20spend%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20days%20here.%20Terrified%20at%20the%20thought%2C%20Thevan%20politely%20declines%20the%20offer.%20But%20Kodumon%20tricks%20him%20into%20starting%20a%20game%2C%20which%20he%20eventually%20wins%2C%20sealing%20Thevan%E2%80%99s%20fate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20world%20in%20Sadasivan%E2%80%99s%20primarily%20black-and-white%20film%20is%20impressively%20atmospheric%20and%20often%20teases%20that%20its%20commentary%20is%20more%20profound%20and%20novel%20than%20it%20is.%20Anyone%20who%20finds%20themselves%20at%20the%20top%20in%20the%20social%20hierarchy%20is%20corrupted%20by%20the%20power%20at%20their%20disposal.%20It%E2%80%99s%20impossible%20for%20the%20oppressed%20to%20make%20good%20on%20their%20promise%2C%20given%20the%20ploys%20of%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20powerful%20are%20enough%20to%20erase%20any%20hard-earned%20progress%20by%20lifting%20a%20finger.%20The%20benevolence%20of%20the%20privileged%20lasts%20only%20till%20they%20can%20utilise%20those%20from%20the%20oppressed%20classes%3A%20either%20for%20their%20labour%2C%20consume%20their%20art%20for%20entertainment%20purposes%2C%20or%20use%20their%20body%20as%20bait%20to%20amass%20even%20more%20riches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESadasivan%E2%80%99s%20film%20takes%20the%20scenic%20route%20to%20the%20social%20justice%20horror%20it%20wants%20to%20be%2C%20with%20the%20pace%20picking%20up%20in%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20second%20hour.%20Mammootty%2C%20whose%20career%20seems%20to%20have%20got%20an%20adrenaline%20hit%20in%20the%20last%20year%2C%20is%20in%20fine%20form%20as%20the%20devious%2C%20%3Cem%3Epaan%3C%2Fem%3E-chewing%20upper-caste%20sorcerer%20with%20stained%20teeth%2C%20making%20promises%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20intend%20to%20keep.%20Arjun%20Ashokan%20and%20Siddharth%20Bharathan%20are%20both%20sincere%20as%20the%20prisoners%20of%20this%20palace%2C%20with%20limitless%20grain%20at%20their%20disposal%2C%20but%20having%20to%20put%20up%20with%20indignity%20%E2%80%93%20something%20that%20could%20cause%20anyone%20to%20lose%20their%20mind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESadasivan%E2%80%99s%20film%20even%20touches%20upon%20it%20in%20a%20later%20portion%20of%20the%20film%2C%20when%20Thevan%20tells%20the%20cook%20he%E2%80%99s%20been%20at%20the%20palace%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20sure%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20cook%20asks%20Thevan%2C%20and%20only%20then%20does%20the%20viewer%20begin%20to%20notice%20how%20Thevan%E2%80%99s%20body%20has%20changed%20since%20he%20set%20foot%20in%20the%20palace.%20He%20also%20can%E2%80%99t%20remember%20his%20name%20anymore.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20chilling%20reminder%20for%20how%20many%20people%20living%20a%20subjugated%20existence%20often%20erase%20their%20identities%20and%20preferences%20in%20their%20own%20head.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ekarma%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20drilled%20into%20them%20is%20obedience%2C%20which%20is%20then%20passed%20from%20one%20generation%20to%20the%20next%2C%20helping%20maintain%20the%20social%20order.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBramayugam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20becomes%20significantly%20more%20literal%20towards%20the%20end%2C%20when%20a%20character%20tells%20another%20about%20how%20the%20%E2%80%98power%E2%80%99%20bestowed%20on%20the%20Potti%20family%20is%20actually%20a%20%E2%80%98curse%E2%80%99%20and%20discourages%20them%20from%20staking%20claim%20to%20it.%20The%20climax%20is%20thrilling%20to%20watch%2C%20but%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20leave%20us%20with%20a%20particularly%20profound%20observation%20of%20its%20own.%20Except%2C%20when%20it%20mentions%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBramayugam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20translates%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98age%20of%20madness%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20when%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20God%20(or%20truth)%20anymore.%20There%E2%80%99s%20no%20space%20for%20decency%2C%20and%20only%20the%20greedy%20and%20twisted%20will%20survive%20this.%20Look%20around%2C%20sound%20familiar%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711024204000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22ht