20be%20reduced%2010%20times%20with%20reusable%20tech%20that%20can%20bring%20down%20costs%20to%20%242%2C000%20per%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20ISRO%20pushing%20to%20master%20the%20reusable%20rocket%20tech%2C%20India's%2021st-century%20Pushpak%20%26quot%3Bvimana%26quot%3B%20is%20ready%20to%20take%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ISRO%20is%20experimenting%20its%20Pushpak%20launch%20vehicle%2C%20resembling%20the%20American%20Space%20Shuttle.%20and%20the%20model%20used%20in%20the%20research%20is%20much%20smaller%20than%20the%20actual%20one.%20A%20sleek%20SUV-sized%20winged%20rocket%20will%20be%20launched%20for%20its%20experimental%20flight%2C%20while%20the%20final%20rocket%20will%20take%20at%20least%2010%20to%2015%20years%20to%20be%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20countries%20to%20attempt%20operational%20flights%20of%20a%20space%20shuttle%20are%20the%20US%2C%20Russia%2C%20France%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20flew%20its%20space%20shuttle%20135%20times%20before%20retiring%20it%20in%202011.%20The%20Russians%20made%20a%20single-space%20shuttle%20-%20Buran%20-%20and%20flew%20it%20into%20space%20once%20in%201989.%20The%20French%20and%20the%20Japanese%20made%20some%20experimental%20flights%2C%20while%20the%20Chinese%20have%20also%20been%20experimenting%20with%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20billionaires%2C%20with%20active%20support%20from%20NASA%2C%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20master%20vertical%20lift-offs%20and%20landings%20of%20recyclable%20rocket%20engines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk's%20SpaceX%20is%20working%20to%20bring%20back%20and%20reuse%20rocket%20engines%2C%20while%20Jeff%20Bezos'%20Blue%20Origin%20successfully%20landed%20its%20New%20Shepard%20rocket%20in%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20key%20technology%20the%20scientists%20at%20the%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20Space%20Centre%20(VSSC)%20had%20to%20develop%20was%20manufacturing%20materials%20that%20can%20withstand%20the%20extremely%20high%20temperatures%20that%20the%20exterior%20of%20the%20vehicle%20faces%20while%20re-entering%20the%20dense%20atmosphere%20after%20journeying%20through%20near%20vacuum%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exterior%20of%20the%20rocket%20becomes%20a%20red-hot%20iron%20plate%20due%20to%20the%20friction%20on%20re-entry.%20To%20withstand%20these%205%2C000-7%2C000%20degree%20Celsius%20temperatures%2C%20scientists%20developed%20very%20lightweight%20heat-resistant%20silica%20tiles%20for%20the%20underbelly%20of%20the%20space%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nose%20cone%20takes%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20high%20temperatures%20and%20is%20made%20of%20a%20special%20carbon-carbon%20composite%20that%20can%20withstand%20high%20temperatures.%20These%20are%20necessary%20to%20protect%20the%20insides%20of%20the%20craft%20where%20the%20temperatures%20should%20not%20breach%2050%20degrees%20Celsius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20heat-resistant%20tiles%20and%20thermal%20coatings%20failed%20on%20the%20American%20Space%20Shuttle%20Columbia%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20death%20of%20Indian-American%20astronaut%20Kalpana%20Chawla%20in%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711022700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F1a50hpko_pushpak-rocket-ndtv_625x300_21_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-india-gives-wing-to-rocket-dreams-heres-why-others-stopped-trials-5283223%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20is%20arduously%20working%20to%20perfect%20a%20winged%20rocket%20even%20as%20most%20global%20efforts%20to%20have%20these%20space%20planes%20have%20come%20to%20naught.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-india-gives-wing-to-rocket-dreams-heres-why-others-stopped-trials-5283223%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-india-gives-wing-to-rocket-dreams-heres-why-others-stopped-trials-5283223%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-india-gives-wing-to-rocket-dreams-heres-why-others-stopped-trials-5283223%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World%20Happiness%20Report%202024%3A%20India%20Ranks%20126th%20Out%20of%20143%20Nations%3B%20Behind%20Pakistan%2C%20Iraq%2C%20Palestine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2FGuava1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIndia%20was%20ranked%20126th%20out%20of%20143%20nations%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fworldhappiness.report%2Fed%2F2024%2Fdifferences-in-life-satisfaction-among-older-adults-in-india%2F%5C%22%3EWorld%20Happiness%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%202024%2C%20a%20global%20happiness%20index%20which%20was%20released%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20March%2020%20to%20mark%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%20International%20Day%20of%20Happiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20behind%20Pakistan%2C%20Libya%2C%20Iraq%2C%20Palestine%20and%20Niger%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%20by%20a%20partnership%20of%20Gallup%2C%20the%20Oxford%20Wellbeing%20Research%20Centre%2C%20the%20UN%20Sustainable%20Development%20Solutions%20Network%2C%20and%20the%20WHR%E2%80%99s%20Editorial%20Board%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EPTI%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Findia-ranks-126th-out-of-143-nations-on-global-happiness-index-602622%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20seventh%20successive%20year%2C%20Finland%20topped%20the%20list%20of%20the%20happiest%20countries%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20other%20countries%20in%20the%20top%20ten%20were%20Denmark%2C%20Iceland%2C%20Sweden%2C%20Israel%2C%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20Norway%2C%20Luxembourg%2C%20Switzerland%20and%20Australia.%20Afghanistan%20was%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPTI%20%3C%2Fem%3Equoted%20from%20the%20report%20that%20older%20age%20is%20associated%20with%20higher%20life%20satisfaction%20in%20India%2C%20%E2%80%9Crefuting%20some%20claims%20that%20the%20positive%20association%20between%20age%20and%20life%20satisfaction%20only%20exists%20in%20high-income%20nations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOlder%20men%20in%20India%20are%20more%20satisfied%20with%20life%20than%20older%20women%20on%20an%20average%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report%2C%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cbut%20when%20taking%20all%20other%20measures%20into%20account%2C%20older%20women%20report%20higher%20life%20satisfaction%20than%20their%20male%20counterparts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-google-query-id%3D%5C%22CNz7mo7whIUDFbaLZgIdaNwLRQ%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20also%20revealed%20that%20older%20adults%20In%20India%20with%20secondary%20or%20higher%20education%20and%20those%20of%20higher%20social%20castes%20reported%20higher%20life%20satisfaction%20compared%20to%20those%20without%20formal%20education%20and%20those%20from%20scheduled%20castes%20and%20scheduled%20tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20older%20population%20is%20the%20second%20largest%20worldwide%2C%20with%20140%20million%20Indians%20aged%2060%20and%20over%2C%20second%20only%20to%20its%20250%20million%20Chinese%20counterparts.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20average%20growth%20rate%20for%20Indians%20aged%2060%20and%20above%20is%20three%20times%20higher%20than%20the%20overall%20population%20growth%20rate%20of%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20mentioned%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3EPTI%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20that%20older%20men%2C%20those%20in%20the%20higher%20age%20groups%2C%20currently%20married%2C%20and%20those%20who%20were%20educated%2C%20report%20higher%20life%20satisfaction%20compared%20to%20their%20respective%20peers.%20Lower%20satisfaction%20with%20living%20arrangements%2C%20perceived%20discrimination%2C%20and%20poor%20self-rated%20health%20were%20important%20factors%20associated%20with%20low%20life%20satisfaction%20am