20raged%20on%20until%20the%20court%20finally%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20residents%2C%20restoring%20their%20long-denied%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20society%20was%20envisioned%20as%20a%20haven%20for%20retirees%20and%20seniors%2C%20offering%20them%20a%20comfortable%20living%20space%20to%20enjoy%20their%20golden%20years.%20Most%20investors%20were%20only%20a%20few%20years%20away%20from%20retirement%2C%20investing%20their%20hard-earned%20money%20with%20hopes%20of%20settling%20into%20their%20new%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20construction%20faced%20several%20legal%20obstacles%2C%20including%20a%20big%20setback%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20court-issued%20stay%20order.%20Spearheaded%20by%20builder%20Sunil%20Uppal%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Uttarakhand%2C%20the%20society%20faced%20complications%20due%20to%20legal%20disputes%20stemming%20from%20Mr%20Uppal's%20other%20projects%20in%20the%20state.%20Mr%20Uppal%20died%20while%20the%20project%20was%20still%20in%20court%2C%20further%20delaying%20the%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComplaints%20from%20Mr%20Uppal's%20projects%20in%20Uttarakhand%20spilled%20over%20to%20affect%20the%20Senior%20Citizens%20Society%2C%20which%20was%20registered%20in%20Dehradun.%20Despite%20a%20court%20order%20for%20registries%20in%202017%2C%20the%20process%20was%20halted%20yet%20again%20due%20to%20allegations%20of%20tax%20evasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20flat%20registries%20for%20over%20100%20flats%2C%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%20845%2C%20in%20the%20society%20finally%20began.%20Residents%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20invested%20in%20these%20flats%20before%20retirement%20when%20the%20average%20price%20ranged%20between%20Rs%206-8%20lakh%2C%20are%20predominantly%20in%20their%2070s%20and%2080s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishi%20Pal%20Singh%2C%20President%20of%20the%20RWA%20Senior%20Citizens%20Society%2C%20recalled%20the%20several%20challenges%20the%20society%20confronted%20over%20the%20years%2C%20from%20legal