20height%3D%5C%222128%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBuying%20a%20house%20can%20be%20a%20good%20investment%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20automatically%20the%20best%20investment.%3Cp%3Exeni4ka%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20you%20can%20sublet%20rooms%20in%20your%20apartment%2C%20you%20can%20make%20passive%20income%20each%20month.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20you%20view%20your%20home%20as%20an%20investment%2C%20remember%20that%20it%20might%20not%20be%20the%20best%20investment.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EYou%20could%20instead%20invest%20that%20money%20in%20stocks%20or%20an%20entrepreneurial%20passive%20income%20stream.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%2035%2C%20more%20than%20half%20of%20my%20friends%20own%20homes.%20Whenever%20I%20find%20myself%20in%20conversation%20with%20those%20people%2C%20they%20are%20quick%20to%20judge%20my%20decision%20to%20be%20a%20renter%20instead%20of%20a%20homeowner.%20I%20try%20to%20explain%20to%20them%20that%20renting%20has%20big%20financial%20benefits%20for%20me.%20I'm%20able%20to%20hunt%20for%20inexpensive%20places%20to%20rent%2C%20and%20I%20avoid%20many%20living%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20I%20have%20no%20intention%20of%20buying%20a%20property%20anytime%20soon%2C%20these%20friends%20like%20to%20tell%20me%20that%20renting%20will%20set%20me%20back%20financially%20and%20it%20will%20always%20hold%20me%20back%20from%20increasing%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-net-worth%5C%22%3Enet%20worth%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20financial%20perks%20that%20come%20with%20owning%20a%20home%2C%20like%20yearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftax-deductions-for-homeowners%5C%22%3Etax%20deductions%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20an%20opportunity%20to%20receive%20a%20big%20return%20on%20your%20investment%20years%20down%20the%20road%2C%20there%20are%20also%20financial%20incentives%20that%20come%20with%20renting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECertified%20financial%20planner%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmanskewealth.com%2Fstaff%2Fchristopher-r-manske%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChristopher%20Manske%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20three%20ways%20that%20renting%20can%20make%20you%20wealthier%20than%20owning%20a%20home%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20Sublet%20out%20your%20rental%20for%20passive%20income%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20your%20rental%20agreement%2C%20Manske%20says%20that%20you%20could%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-ways-to-earn-passive-income%5C%22%3Epassive%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20just%20cover%20your%20rent%20payment%20by%20subletting%20out%20your%20rental.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20renting%20a%20house%20or%20apartment%20with%20multiple%20bedrooms%2C%20you%20can%20sublet%20the%20rooms%20you%20don't%20use.%20Manske%20says%20you%20could%20charge%20a%20higher%20fee%20than%20you%20paid%20so%20that%20you%20can%20not%20only%20cover%20your%20rental%20costs%20but%20make%20money%20on%20top%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20way%2C%20you%20have%20roommates%20coming%20in%20and%20paying%20you%20their%20portion%20of%20rent%2C%20at%20a%20price%20that%20you%20set%2C%20which%20can%20offset%20your%20rental%20costs%20and%20make%20you%20money%20on%20top%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Manske%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20he%20says%20if%20you%20rented%20a%204-bedroom%20unit%20for%20%244%2C000%2C%20you%20could%20charge%20%241%2C500%20per%20room.%20You%20would%20then%20be%20able%20to%20pay%20the%20rent%20and%20earn%20an%20additional%20%242%2C000%20a%20month%20in%20passive%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20live%20in%20one%20of%20those%20rooms%2C%20your%20cost%20of%20living%20could%20be%20covered%20by%20renting%20out%20the%20rooms%20for%20more%20money.%20%26quot%3BThe%20three%20rooms%20add%20up%20to%20%244%2C500%2C%20so%20you%20pay%20nothing%2C%20and%20you're%20making%20%24500%20a%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20Manske%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20you%20could%20do%20something%20similar%20as%20a%20homeowner%2C%20Manske%20says%20the%20main%20difference%20is%20you%20don't%20have%20all%20the%20added%20expenses%20as%20a%20renter%2C%20like%20taxes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhomeowners-insurance%5C%22%3Ehomeowners%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20the%20costs%20associated%20with%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20Be%20more%20strategic%20with%20your%20investments%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20a%20homeowner%2C%20it's%20possible%20your%20property%20will%20appreciate%20over%20time%2C%20which%20means%20you're%20able%20to%20sell%20it%20for%20a%20profit.%20Many%20experts%20recommend%20living%20in%20a%20home%20for%20at%20least%20five%20years%20before%20selling%20it%2C%20so%20you're%20at%20less%20of%20a%20risk%20of%20losing%20money%20on%20the%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManske%20says%20that%20game%20plan%20might%20not%20work%20best%20for%20everyone.%20He%20says%20that%20when%20someone%20owns%20a%20home%2C%20they%20are%20tying%20up%20a%20portion%20of%20their%20capital%20in%20that%20home%2C%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-much-down-payment-for-a-house%5C%22%3Edown%20payment%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-are-mortgage-closing-costs%5C%22%3Eclosing%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20insurance%20and%20taxes%2C%20and%20so%20much%20more.%20If%20you%20take%20out%20a%20mortgage%2C%20you%20have%20to%20put%20money%20toward%20that%20loan%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20just%20owning%20something%20that%20costs%20you%20money%2C%20you%20can%20take%20that%20cash%20and%20put%20it%20into%20another%20income%20producing%20investment%20that%20doesn't%20require%20ongoing%20maintenance%20and%20recurring%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20people%2C%20putting%20money%20into%20a%20house%20might%20make%20less%20sense%20than%20putting%20it%20in%20a%20mixture%20of%20stocks%20and%20bonds%20that%20pay%20enough%20interest%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-dividends-are-taxed%5C%22%3Edividends%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20cover%20rent%20payments%20and%20provide%20extra%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20Use%20the%20money%20to%20invest%20in%20passive%20income%20streams%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20someone%20with%20more%20of%20an%20entrepreneurial%20spirit%2C%20Manske%20suggested%20looking%20into%20ways%20you%20could%20take%20the%20money%20you'd%20use%20for%20a%20down%20payment%20and%20invest%20it%20in%20different%20revenue%20streams%20or%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStarting%20passive%20income%20businesses%20%E2%80%94%20like%20laundromats%2C%20vending%20machines%2C%20or%20anything%20that%20requires%20just%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20attention%20from%20you%20%E2%80%94%20allows%20you%20to%20collect%20an%20income%20stream%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Manske.%20%26quot%3BThat%20way%2C%20you%20can%20collect%20an%20income%20stream%20and%20become%20a%20business%20owner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-find-financial-advisor%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20that%20serve%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%20been%20vetted%20by%20SmartAsset%20and%20is%20held%20to%20a%20fiduciary%20standard%20to%20act%20in%20your%20best%20interests.%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Start%20your%20search%20now.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-renting-could-make-you-wealthier-than-owning-home-2024-03%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711019701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c147bc35e9130019c664c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-renting-could-make-you-wealthier-than-owning-home-2024-03%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Buying%20a%20house%20can%20be%20a%20great%20investment%2C%20but%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20reasons%20to%20consider%20renting%20instead%20%E2%80%94%20and%20potentially%20being%20better%20off%20long-term.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jen%20Glantz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-renting-could-make-you-wealthier-than-owning-home-2024-03%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SBI%20Submits%20All%20Details%20Of%20Poll%20Bonds%20With%20Serial%20Numbers%20To%20Election%20Body%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20rapped%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20has%20submitted%20all%20the%20details%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20The%20data%20includes%20the%20all-important%20serial%20numbers%20for%20the%20bonds%2C%20which%20will%20help%20match%20the%20donors%20with%20the%20political%20parties%20that%20were%20the%20recipients.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SBI%20submitted%20an%20affidavit%20of%20compliance%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Thursday.%20One%20of%20the%20points%20of%20the%20affidavit%20reads%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20respectfully%20submitted%20that%20SBI%20has%20now%20disclosed%20all%20details%20and%20that%20no%20details%20%5Bother%20than%20complete%20account%20numbers%20%26amp%3B%20KYC%20details%5D%20have%20been%20withheld%20from%20disclosure.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20details%20given%20by%20the%20bank%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20uploaded%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20on%20its%20website%20shortly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SBI%20had%20earlier%20given%20two%20lists%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20which%20were%20released%20by%20the%20poll%20panel%20on%20its%20website%20on%20March%2014.%20The%20first%20had%20the%20names%20of%20the%20donors%2C%20the%20denominations%20of%20the%20bonds%2C%20and%20the%20dates%20on%20which%20they%20were%20purchased.%20The%20other%20had%20names%20of%20the%20political%20parties%20as%20well%20as%20the%20denominations%20of%20the%20bonds%20and%20the%20dates%20on%20which%20they%20were%20encashed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20the%20unique%20alphanumeric%20code%2C%20however%2C%20there%20was%20no%20way%20of%20linking%20the%20lists%20and%20finding%20out%20which%20donor%20had%20given%20money%20to%20which%20party.%20The%20alphanumeric%20code%20can%20only%20be%20seen%20using%20ultraviolet%20(UV)%20light.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20asked%20the%20SBI%20to%20disclose%20all%20details%20related%20to%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20including%20the%20serial%20numbers%2C%20by%205%20pm%20today%20and%20also%20file%20an%20affidavit%20to%20that%20effect.%20The%20direction%20had%20come%20in%20response%20to%20a%20petition%20against%20the%20%26quot%3Bincomplete%20data%26quot%3B%20provided%20by%20the%20bank%2C%20which%20is%20India's%20largest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20all%20information%20related%20to%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20be%20disclosed%20which%20is%20in%20your%20possession...%20The%20SBI's%20attitude%20seems%20to%20be%20'you%20tell%20us%20what%20to%20disclose%2C%20we%20will%20disclose'.%20That%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20fair.%20When%20we%20say%20%26quot%3Ball%20details%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20includes%20all%20conceivable%20data...%20All%20details%20should%20come%20out.%20We%20want%20to%20ensure%20that%20nothing%20has%20been%20suppressed%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20affidavit%20on%20Thursday%2C%20which%20bears%20the%20name%20of%20SBI%20Chairman%20Dinesh%20Kumar%20Khara%2C%20the%20bank%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20bears%20repetition%20that%20the%20SBI%20is%20now%20revealing%20information%20%5Balongwith%20that%20already%20disclosed%5D%20which%20will%20show%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20name%20of%20the%20purchaser%20of%20the%20bond%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20denomination%20and%20specific%20number%20of%20the%20bond%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20name%20of%20the%20party%20that%20has%20encashed%20the%20bond%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELast%20four%20digits%20of%20the%20bank%20account%20number%20of%20political%20parties%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20denomination%20and%20number%20of%20the%20bond%20encashed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20also%20asked%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20upload%20the%20details%20once%20it%20got%20them%20from%20the%20SBI%2C%20and%20that%20is%20likely%20to%20happen%20later%20on%20Thursday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20had%20been%20termed%20unconstitutional%20and%20arbitrary%20and%20struck%20down%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20February%2015.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711019700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2Foc23r498_sbi-state-bank-of-india-reuters_625x300_10_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstate-bank-of-india-submits-all-details-of-electoral-bonds-with-serial-numbers-to-election-commission-5282315%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20being%20rapped%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20has%20submitted%20all%20the%20details%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement