3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-to-launch-bjp-campaign-in-karnataka-from-congress-chiefs-turf-5243115%5C%22%3EKarnataka%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20traditionally%20characterised%20as%20the%20sole%20region%20where%20the%20Lotus%20blooms%20in%20terms%20of%20electoral%20dividends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20states%20and%20one%20union%20territory%20collectively%20represent%20over%20130%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20For%20a%20party%20with%20the%20ambitious%20battle%20cry%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fabki-baar-400-paar-for-lok-sabha-polls-given-by-people-not-bjp-pm-modi-5151650%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAbki%20Baar%20400%20Paar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20(to%20win%20over%20400%20of%20the%20543%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies)%2C%20rallying%20support%20from%20all%20directions%20becomes%20imperative.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20the%20BJP%20holds%2025%20of%20the%2029%20seats%20it%20won%20in%20the%20current%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20the%20remaining%20seats%20are%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-launches-projects-worth-rs-7-200-crore-in-telangana-highlights-centres-focus-5179675%5C%22%3ETelangana%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20party%20drew%20a%20blank%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Multi-Pronged%20Approach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20strategy%20to%20maximise%20its%20presence%20in%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20encompasses%20several%20distinct%20strands.%20Following%20the%20remarkable%20performance%20in%20the%20November-December%20polls%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20party%20decided%20to%20shift%20its%20focus%20to%20the%20South.%20Executing%20this%20strategy%2C%20PM%20Modi%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20other%20party%20leaders%20have%20engaged%20in%20extensive%20outreach%20efforts%2C%20making%20frequent%20trips%20to%20unveil%20projects%20and%20address%20issues%20concerning%20state%20governments'%20performance%2C%20thus%20providing%20some%20food%20for%20thought%20to%20the%20electorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20general%20elections%20looming%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20forged%20coalitions%20in%20several%20states%2C%20some%20of%20which%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20chip%20away%20at%20minor%20portions%20of%20the%20political%20pie.%20In%20others%2C%20it%20aims%20to%20establish%20a%20foothold.%20The%20following%20paragraphs%20delve%20into%20state-specific%20tactics%20and%20their%20potential%20impact%20as%20regional%20parties%20in%20the%20South%20gear%20up%20to%20challenge%20the%20BJP's%20pole%20position%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%3A%20A%20Triangular%20Contest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20align%20with%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)-Jana%20Sena%20alliance%20holds%20the%20potential%20to%20win%20more%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20This%20is%20significant%20also%20because%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20concurrently%20elects%20a%20new%20assembly.%20Political%20dynamics%20revolve%20around%20the%20dominant%20YSR%20Congress%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%2C%20who%20is%20now%20facing%20strains%20associated%20with%20prolonged%20incumbency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20challenges%20posed%20by%20Nara%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20TDP%20and%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20Jana%20Sena%2C%20Reddy%20also%20faces%20competition%20from%20a%20resurgent%20Congress%2C%20led%20in%20the%20state%20by%20his%20estranged%20sister%20Y.S.%20Sharmila.%20In%20this%20triangular%20contest%2C%20the%20BJP%20aims%20to%20capitalise%20on%20PM%20Modi's%20image%2C%20bolstering%20the%20coalition's%20prospects%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKerala%3A%20Carving%20Out%20A%20Space%20Of%20Its%20Own%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20continued%20activity%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20and%20its%20longstanding%20influence%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20struggled%20to%20achieve%20significant%20electoral%20success%20in%20this%20state.%20However%2C%20by%20expanding%20its%20outreach%20to%20the%20Christian%20community%2C%20the%20party%20aims%20to%20secure%20a%20portion%20of%20their%20votes%2C%20along%20with%20those%20of%20the%20Hindu%20community%2C%20thus%20carving%20out%20a%20political%20space%20that's%20distinct%20from%20that%20of%20the%20dominant%20United%20Democratic%20Front%20(UDF)%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20as%20well%20as%20that%20of%20the%20Left%20Democratic%20Front%20heralded%20by%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India-Marxist%20(CPI-M).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20endeavour%20may%20seem%20ambitious%2C%20one%20can%20trust%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20to%20stir%20the%20placid%20backwaters%20and%20persist%20in%20their%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETamil%20Nadu%3A%20A%20Flurry%20Of%20Alliances%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20gained%20attention%20with%20the%20BJP's%20announcement%20of%20a%20coalition%20with%20the%20Pattali%20Makkal%20Katchi%20(PMK)%2C%20founded%20by%20Dr.%20S.%20Ramadoss%20and%20now%20led%20by%20his%20son%2C%20Dr.%20Anbumani%20Ramadoss%2C%20a%20former%20Union%20Minister.%20The%20PMK%20previously%20held%20power%20in%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20government%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Behari%20Vajpayee.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20allied%20with%20smaller%20parties%20like%20the%20Indhiya%20Jananayaga%20Katchi%20(IJK)%20and%20the%20Amma%20Makkal%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AMMK)%2C%20many%20of%20which%20represent%20specific%20castes%20traditionally%20aligned%20with%20dominant%20Dravidian%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20move%20by%20the%20BJP%20aims%20to%20build%20a%20coalition%20that%20could%20potentially%20increase%20the%20party's%20vote%20share%2C%20establishing%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20Dravidian%20majors%2C%20with%20the%20potential%20to%20attract%20factions%20from%20the%20fragmented%20AIADMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETelangana%3A%20Leveraging%20Modi's%20Popularity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20significant%20momentum%20generated%20by%20its%20former%20state%20unit%20chief%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20prior%20to%20the%20assembly%20elections%20last%20year%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20adopted%20a%20different%20strategy%20in%20Telangana%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20It%20is%20now%20contesting%20alone%2C%20leveraging%20PM%20Modi's%20popularity%20and%20aiming%20to%20surpass%20the%20four%20seats%20it%20won%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKarnataka%3A%20Fertile%20Ground%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20setbacks%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20last%20summer%2C%20the%20BJP%20seeks%20to%20capitalise%20on%20its%20alliance%20with%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20(JDS)%20led%20by%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20H.D.%20Deve%20Gowda.%20Given%20that%20the%20JD(S)%20represents%20the%20Vokkaligas%20and%20the%20BJP%20commands%20support%20from%20the%20dominant%20Lingayat%20community%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20internal%20dynamics%20within%20the%20Congress%2C%20Karnataka%20presents%20a%20fertile%20ground%20for%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20is%20vigorously%20pursuing%20its%20agenda%20in%20southern%20Indian%20states%2C%20aiming%20to%20shed%20its%20perception%20as%20a%20Hindi-speaking%20party%20and%20emerge%20as%20a%20political%20entity%20with%20a%20pan-India%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(K.V.%20Prasad%20is%20a%20senior%20Delhi-based%20journalist.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711018980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F4kovpt5_pm-modi_625x300_27_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fon-bjp-and-its-determined-push-beyond-the-vindhyas-5282752%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20a%20party%20with%20the%2