d-tomorrow-as-scheduledexclusive%2Farticleshow%2F108678914.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108678914.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EWith%20only%20a%20day%20left%20for%20its%20release%2C%20Randeep%20Hooda's%20directorial%20debut%20'Swatantrya%20Veer%20Savarkar'%20is%20still%20struggling%20to%20get%20its%20censor%20certificate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Body%20Massager%20Can't%20Be%20Categorised%20As%20Adult%20Sex%20Toy%2C%20Be%20Prohibited%3A%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20body%20massager%20cannot%20be%20categorised%20as%20an%20adult%20sex%20toy%20and%20hence%20cannot%20be%20included%20in%20the%20list%20of%20items%20prohibited%20for%20import%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Girish%20Kulkarni%20and%20Kishor%20Sant%20on%20Wednesday%20quashed%20an%20order%20passed%20by%20the%20Customs%20department%20confiscating%20consignments%20containing%20body%20massagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commissioner%20of%20Customs%20had%20confiscated%20the%20goods%20claiming%20that%20the%20body%20massagers%20could%20be%20used%20as%20adult%20sex%20toys%20and%20such%20items%20are%20prohibited%20for%20import.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpining%20that%20a%20body%20massager%20could%20be%20used%20as%20an%20adult%20sex%20toy%20was%20clearly%20the%20figment%20of%20imagination%20of%20the%20Commissioner%20of%20Customs%2C%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20dismissed%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20Commissioner%20of%20Customs%2C%20challenging%20a%20May%202023%20order%20passed%20by%20the%20Central%20Excise%20and%20Service%20Tax%20Appellate%20Tribunal%20whereby%20the%20Custom%20department's%20order%20confiscating%20consignments%20containing%20body%20massagers%20was%20set%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commissioner%20of%20Customs%20as%20adjudicating%20officer%20had%20in%20April%202022%20refused%20to%20clear%20the%20consignment%20containing%20body%20massagers%20noting%20that%20they%20were%20adult%20sex%20toys%20and%20hence%20prohibited%20for%20import%20as%20per%20the%20Customs%20notification%20issued%20in%20January%201964.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20findings%20recorded%20by%20the%20commissioner%20are%20%26quot%3Bpeculiar%20and%20clearly%20appear%20to%20be%20quite%20astonishing%20and%20too%20far-fetched%2C%20when%20he%20reduces%20in%20writing%20his%20vivid%20imagination%20on%20what%20an%20equipment%20for%20a%20body%20massage%20would%20be%20and%20more%20particularly%20on%20his%20perception%20on%20the%20perceived%20uses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20clearly%20the%20figment%20of%20the%20Commissioner's%20imagination%20and%2For%20his%20personal%20perception%20that%20the%20goods%20are%20prohibited%20items%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20body%20massagers%20are%20traded%20in%20domestic%20markets%20and%20are%20not%20regarded%20as%20prohibited%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20Commissioner%20(adjudicating%20officer)%20had%20failed%20to%20act%20as%20a%20prudent%20official%20who%20would%20be%20expected%20to%20act%20reasonably%20while%20deciding%20the%20issue%20of%20clearance%20of%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Customs%20Commissioner%20had%20also%20relied%20on%20section%20292(2)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20which%20says%20any%20book%2C%20pamphlet%2C%20paper%2C%20and%20drawing%20or%20any%20other%20objects%20that%20is%20deemed%20to%20be%20obscene%20if%20it%20is%20lascivious%20or%20appeals%20to%20the%20prurient%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%2C%20however%2C%20said%20machines%20like%20massagers%20certainly%20cannot%20be%20compared%20with%20the%20companion%20items%20in%20the%20said%20entries%20which%20are%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20book%2C%20pamphlet%2C%20paper%2C%20drawing%2C%20painting%2C%20representation%2C%20figure%20or%20article%20and%20so%20on%20that%20are%20prohibited%20under%20the%20notification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAggrieved%20by%20the%20Commissioner's%20order%2C%20the%20owners%20of%20the%20consignment%20had%20approached%20the%20tribunal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tribunal%2C%20while%20setting%20aside%20the%20Commissioner's%20order%2C%20severely%20criticised%20the%20same%20and%20said%20the%20view%20taken%20by%20the%20Commissioner%20to%20categorise%20the%20body%20massager%20as%20an%20adult%20sex%20toy%20was%20purely%20the%20officer's%20imagination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commissioner%20had%20claimed%20that%20before%20deciding%20to%20prohibit%20the%20goods%2C%20the%20opinion%20of%20experts%20was%20taken%20who%20had%20opined%20the%20body%20massagers%20could%20be%20subjected%20to%20other%20uses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20however%2C%20said%20merely%20because%20the%20goods%20could%20be%20subjected%20to%20an%20alternative%20use%20cannot%20be%20the%20test%20to%20hold%20that%20they%20were%20prohibited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20appears%20that%20such%20experts%20clearly%20opined%20that%20although%20undoubtedly%20the%20item%20as%20imported%20was%20a%20body%20massager%2C%20however%2C%20it%20was%20also%20their%20opinion%20that%20the%20item%20could%20also%20be%20used%20for%20the%20purpose%20which%20the%20Commissioner%20contemplated%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20dismissed%20the%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20Commissioner%20of%20Customs%20and%20upheld%20the%20tribunal%20order.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711018140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22