%20company%20previously%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdollar-general-low-price-strategy-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20stores%20tend%20to%20carry%20around%2011%2C000%20to%2012%2C000%20SKUs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20so-called%20%26quot%3Blimited%20selection%26quot%3B%20retailer%2C%20Dollar%20General's%20count%20is%20a%20mere%20fraction%20of%20the%20typical%20US%20supermarket%2C%20which%20offers%20about%2030%2C000%20to%2040%2C000%2C%20or%20a%20Walmart%20Supercenter%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finventory-management.com%2Finventory-management%2Finventory-management-at-walmart%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fa%3E%20carries%20more%20than%20140%2C000%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20inches%20Dollar%20General%20closer%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-the-costco-star-of-death-means-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECostco's%20time-tested%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20finding%20savings%20through%20simplicity%20%E2%80%94%20the%20wholesale%20club%20famously%20keeps%20its%20SKU%20count%20to%20around%204%2C000%20in%20its%20warehouses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20Todd%20Vasos%20hinted%20at%20how%20this%20looks%20in%20practice%20when%20he%20previewed%20the%20move%20in%20Dollar%20General's%20earnings%20call%20last%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20may%20have%20five%20or%20six%20different%20variants%20of%20mayonnaise%20on%20the%20shelf%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20easily%20drop%20one%20or%20two%20of%20those.%20The%20consumer%20is%20not%20going%20to%20know%20the%20difference.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20each%20flavor%2C%20color%2C%20or%20size%20of%20a%20product%20requires%20a%20unique%20SKU%2C%20there's%20often%20a%20fair%20amount%20of%20room%20for%20retailers%20to%20focus%20on%20a%20crowd%20favorite%20and%20skip%20the%20hassle%20of%20trying%20to%20match%20everyone's%20unique%20preferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimplifying%20the%20selection%20also%20can%20drive%20more%20sales%20toward%20higher%20volume%20items%2C%20which%20can%20improve%20economies%20of%20scale%2C%20GlobalData%20retail%20analyst%20Neil%20Saunders%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLow%20SKU%20counts%20with%20high%20volumes%20is%20a%20model%20that%20serves%20a%20lot%20of%20price-focused%20retailers%20very%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BCostco%20uses%20this%2C%20as%20does%20Aldi.%20It's%20all%20about%20leveraging%20efficiency%20to%20reduce%20costs%20which%20enables%20lower%20prices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20retailers%20need%20to%20make%20cuts%20with%20care%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20don't%20eliminate%20items%20that%20customers%20are%20especially%20fond%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20fewer%20options%20may%20come%20as%20a%20relief%20to%20some%20shoppers%20suffering%20from%20decision%20fatigue%2C%20as%20any%20Costco%20diehard%20will%20tell%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20Costco%20shows%2C%20retailers%20can%20still%20offer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-buy-at-costco-according-to-superfans-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20staggering%20range%20of%20product%20categories%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20loading%20up%20on%20an%20infinite%20variety%20within%20particular%20products%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20benefits%20of%20simplifying%20the%20selection%20also%20extend%20to%20store%20staff%20and%20the%20company's%20distribution%20teams%2C%20Vasos%20said%2C%20since%20that's%20one%20less%20product%20that%20has%20to%20be%20shipped%2C%20tracked%2C%20and%20stocked%20on%20a%20shelf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20simplification%20could%20boost%20the%20retailer's%20efforts%20to%20clean%20up%20its%20stores%3A%20Some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdollar-general-stores-closing-fire-code-violations-too-much-stuff-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3