nor%20was%20%26quot%3Bdefying%20the%20Supreme%20Court%26quot%3B%20and%20asked%20the%20Centre%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Governor%20does%20not%20follow%20the%20Constitution%2C%20what%20does%20the%20government%20do%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justice%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Justice%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20has%20now%20given%20the%20Governor%20a%20day's%20time%20till%20tomorrow%20to%20appoint%20DMK's%20K%20Ponmudi%20as%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MK%20Stalin%20government%20has%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20after%20Mr%20Ravi%20refused%20to%20re-induct%20Mr%20Ponmudi%20into%20the%20state%20cabinet%2C%20saying%20it%20would%20be%20against%20Constitutional%20morality.%20Mr%20Ponmudi%20was%20disqualified%20as%20an%20MLA%20after%20the%20Madras%20High%20Court%20recently%20reversed%20his%20acquittal%20in%20an%20assets%20case.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20paused%20his%20conviction%20and%20the%20sentence%20of%20a%20two-year%20jail%20term.%20The%20state%20government%20had%20then%20moved%20to%20reinstate%20him%20as%20minister%2C%20but%20the%20Governor%20stressed%20that%20his%20conviction%20has%20only%20been%20suspended%20and%20not%20set%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20do%20not%20hear%20from%20your%20person%20tomorrow%2C%20we%20will%20pass%20an%20order%20directing%20the%20Governor%20to%20act%20according%20to%20the%20constitution.%20We%20are%20seriously%20concerned%20about%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Governor%20and%20his%20behaviour.%20He%20has%20no%20business%20to%20do%20this.%20He%20is%20taking%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20keeping%20eyes%20open%20and%20tomorrow%20we%20will%20decide.%20We%20are%20seriously%20concerned%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20doubled%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20the%20Governor%20is%20%26quot%3Bdefying%20the%20Supreme%20Court%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThose%20who%20have%20advised%20him%20have%20not%20advised%20him%20properly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20may%20have%20a%20different%20perspective%20of%20the%20man%2F%20minister%2C%20but%20we%20have%20to%20go%20by%20the%20constitutional%20law.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20says%20we%20want%20to%20appoint%20this%20person%2C%20the%20Governor%20should%20do%20so%20as%20part%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20democracy.%20He's%20a%20ceremonial%20head%20of%20the%20state.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Pardiwala%20said%20that%20once%20a%20conviction%20is%20stayed%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20cannot%20say%20that%20you%20are%20tainted%2C%20there%20is%20no%20blemish%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ravi's%20refusal%20to%20appoint%20Mr%20Ponmudi%20as%20minister%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20series%20of%20face-offs%20between%20his%20office%20and%20the%20MK%20Stalin%20government%20after%20he%20took%20over%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Governor%20in%202021.%C2%A0The%20DMK%20government%20has%20repeatedly%20accused%20him%20of%20creating%20hurdles%20in%20its%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20state%20government%20had%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20clearing%20Bills.%20The%20court%20had%20then%20said%20the%20Governor%20must%20act%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20Council%20of%20Ministers.%20The%20tussle%20had%20also%20reached%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%2C%20when%20Chief%20Minister%20Stalin%20wrote%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20last%20year%2C%20seeking%20Mr%20Ravi's%20removal%20from%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711016340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F5ftmsqr_cji-rn-ravi_625x300_21_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-pulls-up-tamil-nadu-governor-for-not-appointing-minister-says-its-seriously-concerned-with-his-conduct-5282183%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Governor%20RN%20Ravi%20