0Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Sajjad%20Hussain%2C%20a%20member%20of%20KDA%20who%20contested%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20from%20Ladakh%2C%20said%20that%20the%20grouping%20will%20join%20Wangchuk%20from%20March%2024%20to%20March%2027%20as%20the%20talks%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20have%20failed%20to%20address%20their%20demands%20of%20Sixth%20Schedule%20rights%20for%20Ladakh%20and%20restoration%20of%20its%20statehood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20issue%20of%20statehood%20and%20Sixth%20Schedule%20are%20close%20to%20the%20hearts%20of%20Ladakhis.%20It%20is%20not%20just%20our%20demand.%20It%20is%20a%20popular%20sentiment%20and%20aspiration%20of%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20and%20we%20will%20take%20this%20struggle%20to%20its%20logical%20conclusion%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hussain%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20prominent%20social%20activist%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20massive%20protest%20was%20held%20in%20Kargil%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20March%2020%2C%20following%20a%20half-day%20shutdown%20call%20by%20the%20KDA%20in%20support%20of%20Wangchuk%20who%20has%20been%20fasting%20in%20Leh%20for%20the%20last%2015%20days%20braving%20extreme%20sub-zero%20conditions%20under%20open%20skies.%20Thousands%20of%20people%20from%20Ladakh%20have%20joined%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22With%20Ladakh%20as%20UT%2C%20Local%20Youth%20Lost%20All%20Access%20to%20Public%20Employment%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwith-ladakh-as-ut-local-youth-lost-all-access-to-public-employment%5C%22%3EWith%20Ladakh%20as%20UT%2C%20Local%20Youth%20Lost%20All%20Access%20to%20Public%20Employment%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShouting%20slogans%2C%20the%20protesters%20assembled%20in%20the%20main%20market%20of%20Kargil%20which%20resonated%20with%20demands%20of%20restoration%20of%20democracy%20and%20statehood%20and%20inclusion%20of%20Ladakh%20in%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsghar%20Ali%20Karbalai%2C%20a%20co-