lls-it-ministry-to-immediately-stop-sending-viksit-bharat-messages-with-modis-letter%5C%22%3Eordered%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20to%20halt%20its%20WhatsApp%20campaign%20with%20a%20letter%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%20asking%20for%20feedback.%20Terming%20the%20campaign%20a%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20(MCC)%20violation%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20ordered%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20to%20ensure%20no%20more%20such%20messages%20are%20sent%20by%20the%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20was%20reacting%20to%20the%20MCC%20violation%20complaints%20filed%20across%20the%20country%2C%20including%20one%20filed%20in%20Chandigarh.%20The%20Chandigarh%20authorities%20referred%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fprima-facie-mcc-violation-chandigarh-authorities-refer-modis-mass-whatsapp-message-to-ec%5C%22%3EMCC%20violation%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20after%20receiving%20it%20via%20the%20C-Vigil%20app%2C%20where%20a%20voter%20alleged%20misuse%20of%20government%20funds%20for%20a%20political%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20441px)%2085vw%2C%20441px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21144000%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-1.40.54-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22441%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21144000%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-1.40.54-PM.jpeg%201049w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21144000%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-1.40.54-PM-262x300.jpeg%20262w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21144000%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-1.40.54-PM-895x1024.jpeg%20895w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-702641%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22505%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20enquiry%20from%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20has%20explained%20that%20the%20WhatsApp%20messages%20were%20been%20sent%20on%20March%2015%2C%20before%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20polls.%20The%20ministry%20explained%20that%20multiple%20people%20might%20have%20received%20it%20afterwards%20because%20of%20WhatsApp%E2%80%99s%20system%20architecture%20and%20network%20limitations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20while%20ordering%20a%20stop%20of%20the%20campaign%2C%20ordered%20for%20a%20compliance%20report%20to%20be%20shared%20with%20its%20office.%20In%20his%20letter%20to%20MeITY%2C%20Narendra%20N.%20Butolia%2C%20senior%20principal%20secretary%20of%20ECI%2C%20ordered%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Commission%20has%20received%20complaints%20from%20various%20quarters%20that%20such%20messages%20are%20still%20being%20delivered%20on%20citizens%E2%80%99%20phones.%20Since%20the%20MCC%20is%20now%20in%20force%2C%20you%20are%20hereby%20directed%20to%20ensure%20forthwith%20that%20no%20further%20delivery%20of%20%E2%80%98WhatsApp%20messages%E2%80%99%20take%20place%20during%20MCC%20period.%20A%20compliance%20report%20in%20this%20regard%20may%20be%20sent%20immediately.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20halted%20this%20exercise%2C%20it%20did%20not%20go%20further%20into%20enquiring%20about%20privacy%20violations%20of%20voters%20by%20MeITY.%20It%20is%20unclear%20on%20what%20basis%20the%20messages%20were%20sent%20to%20different%20people%20across%20the%20world%20by%20MeITY.%20The%20messages%20being%20delivered%20to%20foreign%20nationals%20has%20raised%20many%20questions%20on%20privacy%20violations%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20has%20not%20really%20engaged%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20role%20of%20personal%20data%20in%20elections.%20With%20the%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%202023%20having%20been%20passed%20by%20the%20parliament%2C%20the%20ECI%20will%20be%20the%20body%20that%20is%20responsible%20for%20any%20privacy%20violations%20with%20regards%20to%20personal%20data%20being%20used%20in%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20has%20to%20look%20into%20the%20role%20of%20private%20campaigns%20over%20social%20media%20and%20WhatsApp%20ideally%2C%20which%20the%20commission%20has%20been%20ignoring%20to%20regulate.%20Any%20complaints%20to%20chief%20electoral%20officers%20in%20the%20past%20over%20political%20messaging%20over%20phone%20calls%20and%20through%20communications%20apps%20have%20been%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskodali%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711012582000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21144203%2Figor-omilaev-gVQLAbGVB6Q-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fas-ec-ends-modis-whatsapp-campaign-questions-on-personal-contact-database-remain%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20unclear%20on%20what%20basis%20the%20messages%20were%20sent%20to%20different%20people%20across%20the%20world%20by%20MeITY.%20The%20messages%20being%20delivered%20to%20foreign%20nationals%20has%20raised%20many%20questions%20on%20privacy%20violations%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fas-ec-ends-modis-whatsapp-campaign-questions-on-personal-contact-database-remain%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alanna-Ivor%20McCray%20drop%20gender%20reveal%20video%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711012365000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fst