lace-on-earth-5281883%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Stays%20Union%20Government's%20Notification%20on%20PIB%20Fact-Check%20Unit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F21234509%2FUntitled-design-86-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Thursday%2C%20March%2021%20ordered%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20notification%20of%20Union%20government%20designating%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%E2%80%99s%20fact-check%20arm%20as%20the%20Fact-Checking%20Unit%20(FCU)%20under%20the%20amended%20Information%20Technology%20Rules%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLiveLawIndia%2Fstatus%2F1770718609486045280%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELive%20Law%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CQuite%20apart%20from%20the%20statement%20made%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20the%20challenges%20to%20the%20rule%20involves%20serious%20constitutional%20questions.%20The%20impact%20of%20Rule%203(1)(b)(v)%20on%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20would%20fall%20for%20analysis%20by%20the%20High%20Court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20comprising%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20Justices%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20we%20are%20clearly%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20notification%20dated%20March%2020%2C%202024%2C%20issued%20by%20the%20Union%20Govt%20after%20the%20rejection%20of%20the%20application%20for%20interim%20relief%2C%20would%20need%20to%20be%20stayed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stay%20will%20be%20valid%20till%20the%20disposal%20of%20the%20proceedings%20challenging%20validity%20of%20the%20fact-checking%20unit%20before%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20said%20that%20there%20will%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fno-interim-stay-notification-fact-checking-unit-bombay-hc%5C%22%3Eno%20interim%20stay%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Union%20government%20notifying%20the%20fact-checking%20unit%2C%20a%20month%C2%A0after%20a%20two-judge%20bench%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbombay-hc-split-verdict-petition-it-amendment-rules%5C%22%3Edelivered%20a%20split%20verdict%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20specific%20rule%20dealing%20with%20said%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2020%2C%20the%20Union%20electronics%20and%20IT%20ministry%20had%20notified%20the%20FCU%20as%20a%20statutory%20body%20with%20powers%20to%20flag%20what%20it%20believes%20is%20false%20information%20related%20to%20the%20Central%20government%20and%20its%20agencies%20on%20social%20media%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitions%20were%20filed%20by%20Kunal%20Kamra%2C%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%20and%20Association%20of%20Indian%20Magazines%20challenging%20the%20refusal%20of%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20to%20stay%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20IT%20Rules%202023.%20As%20per%20a%3Cem%3E%20Live%20Law%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-kunal-kamra-editors-guild-notifying-fact-check-unit-it-rules-2023-252998%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20CJI-led%20bench%20was%20of%20the%20view%20that%20there%20existed%20prima%20facie%20grounds%20for%20staying%20the%20notification%20dated%20March%2020%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20impugned%20Rules%20operational.%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20in%20the%20past%2C%20there%20are%20serious%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20PIB%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20function%20as%20an%20independent%20body%20that%20will%20conduct%20fair%20fact-checks.%20Researchers%20at%20the%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fout-of-nearly-1-2-lakh-queries-in-3-years-pibs-fact-check-unit-acted-on-1223%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20PIB%20reveals%20having%20received%20nearly%201.2%20lakh%20requests%20for%20fact%20checking%20information%20on%20the%20internet%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20i.e.%20since%20April%202020%2C%20whereas%20it%20has%20only%20acted%20upon%201%2C223%20of%20them%20%E2%80%93%20a%20modest%201%25%20action%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711010131000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F21234509%2FUntitled-design-86-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-stays-union-governments-notification-on-pib-fact-check-unit%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20March%2020%2C%20the%20Union%20electronics%20and%20IT%20ministry%20had%20notified%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau's%20Fact%20Check%20Unit%20as%20a%20statutory%20body%20with%20powers%20to%20flag%20what%20it%20believes%20is%20false%20information%20related%20to%20the%20Central%20government%20and%20its%20agencies%20on%20social%20media%20sites.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-stays-union-governments-notification-on-pib-fact-check-unit%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taiwan%20Man%20Persuades%20Friend%20To%20Get%20Amputation%20For%20%241.3%20Million%20Scam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Taiwan%20university%20student%20who%20had%20his%20legs%20amputated%20in%20the%20hopes%20of%20winning%20a%20%241.3%20million%20insurance%20claim%20has%20been%20arrested%20on%20suspicion%20of%20fraud%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaiwan-student-convinced-friend-amputate-legs-insurance-scam-prosecutors-2024-3%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cib.npa.gov.tw%2Fch%2Fapp%2Fnews%2Fview%3Fmodule%3Dnews%26id%3D1885%26serno%3D8a38a1f3-3396-4553-a36b-d08984d3ec79%23%5C%22%3ETaiwan%20Criminal%20Investigation%20Bureau%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20the%2023-year-old%2C%20who%20goes%20only%20by%20his%20last%20name%20Zhang%2C%20forced%20himself%20to%20have%20a%20double%20amputation%20after%20he%20put%20his%20feet%20in%20a%20bucket%20of%20dry%20ice%20for%20more%20than%2010%20hours%2C%20which%20caused%20frostbite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%20Liao%2C%20a%20friend%20of%20Zhang%20from%20high%20school%2C%20influenced%20him%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20scam.%20Investigators%20said%20that%20Liao%20lost%20money%20on%20cryptocurrency%20and%20misled%20Zhang%20into%20signing%20a%20legal%20document%20obligating%20Zhang%20to%20pay%20almost%20%24800%2C000.%20He%20also%20told%20Zhang%20that%20some%20gangsters%20were%20after%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%2C%20which%20is%20translated%20from%20Mandarin%2C%20claims%20that%20on%20January%2026%2C%202023%2C%20Zhang%20got%20frostbite%20while%20riding%20a%20motorbike%20with%20his%20friend%20Liao%20in%20Taipei.%20The%20prosecution%20said%20that%20a%20few%20days%20before%20the%20incident%2C%20he%20filed%20for%20life%2C%20health%2C%20and%20accident%20insurance.%20The%20sum%20of%20the%20insurance%20policies%20was%20%241.3%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20the%20two%20returned%20to%20Liao's%20house%2C%20Zhang%20soaked%20his%20feet%20in%20dry%20ice.%20He%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20nearby%20hospital%20after%20the%20foot%20soaking%2C%20where%20medical%20personnel%20thought%20his%20wounds%20were%20fake%2C%20according%20to%20the%20prosecution.%20According%20to%20the%20release%2C%20the%20medical%20staff%20reported%20that%20although%20the%20patient's%20feet%20were%20frostbitten%2C%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Bneat%20and%20symmetrical%26quot%3B%20injuries%20and%20%26quot%3Bno%20socks%20or%20shoe%20marks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20reported%20that%20the%20weather%20on%20the%20night%20of%20January%2026%20was%20%26quot%3Bnowhere%20close%20to%20below%20freezing.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BAs%20Taiwan%20is%20a%20subtropical%20region%2C%20cases%20of%20severe%20frostbite%20requiring%20amputation%20are%20unheard%20of%20due%20to%20natural%20climatic%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bureau%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZhang%20suffered%20frostbite%20injuries%20which%20necessitated%20the%20amputation%20of%20both%20legs%20below%20the%20calf.%20Nonetheless%2C%20the%20prosecutors%20said%20that%20Zhang's%20case%20was%20reported%20to%20the%20authorities.%20Further%2C%20the%20plastic%20bucket%20that%20was%20used%20to%20freeze%20Zhang's%20feet%2C%20insurance%20papers%2C%20a%20white%20polystyrene%20box%20containing%20dry%20ice%2C%20eight%20cell%20phones%2C%20and%20electronic%20devices%20were%20discovered%20by%20police%20during%20their%20investigation%20of%20Zhang%20and%20Liao%20in%20November.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20bureau%2C%20Liao%20and%20Zhang%20were%20both%20charged%20with%20fraud%20and%20aiding%20and%20abetting%20serious%20injury%20after%20their%20detention%20on%20January%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authorities%20said%20that%20Zhang%20received%20one%20insurance%20payout%20of%20%247%2C200%2C%20however%2C%20it%20will%20be%20seized.%20The%20insurance%20providers%20cancelled%20the%20other%20claims%20filed%20following%20the%20incident%20due%20to%20the%20short%20period%20between%20receiving%20the%20policies%20and%20filing%20them%2C%20according%20to%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711009860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F2nadkba_taiwan-criminal-bureau-_625x300_21_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftaiwan-man-persuades-friend-to-get-legs-amputated-for-1-3-million-insurance-scam-5281812%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Zhang%20suffered%20frostbite%20injuries%20which%20necessitated%20the%20amputation%20of%20both%20legs%20below%20the%20calf.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftaiwan-man-persuades-friend-to-get-legs-amputated-for-1-3-million-insurance-scam-5281812%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftaiwan-man-persuades-friend-to-get-legs-amputated-for-1-3-million-insurance-scam-5281812%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftaiwan-man-persuades-friend-to-get-legs-amputated-for-1-3-million-insurance-scam-5281812%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Aruna%20and%20Asaf%20Ali%20Found%20the%20Balance%20in%20Their%20Marriage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21120337%2FAruna-Asaf-Ali.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EExcerpted%20with%20permission%20from%20%3C%2Fem%3ECircles%20of%20Freedom%3A%20Friendship%2C%20Love%20and%20Loyalty%20in%20The%20Indian%20National%20Struggle%3Cem%3E%20by%20T.C.A.%20Raghavan%2C%20published%20by%20Juggernaut.%20The%20book%20looks%20at%20the%20national%20movement%20from%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20characters%20seen%20as%20more%20%E2%80%98marginal%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20explores%20through%20their%20stories%20and%20their%20relationships%20with%20each%20other%2C%20issues%20such%20as%20women%E2%80%99s%20lives%20in%20that%20period%2C%20the%20paradox%20of%20the%20liberal%20moderate%20Muslim%2C%20the%20impact%20the%20freedom%20movement%20had%20on%20marriages%2C%20and%20perhaps%20most%20importantly%20what%20the%20Independence%20movement%20looked%20like%20for%20people%20with%20a%20ring-side%20view%20of%20it%20but%20who%20weren%E2%80%99t%20at%20its%20centre.%20The%20following%20extract%20is%20about%20Aruna%20Asaf%20Ali%E2%80%99s%20marriage%20with%20Asaf%20Ali.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutrage%20and%20criticism%20apart%2C%20the%20marriage%20%5Bbetween%20Aruna%20Gangulee%20and%20Asaf%20Ali%5D%20faced%20other%20more%20personal%20hurdles%20before%20it%20found%20its%20balance.%20Asaf%20%E2%80%99s%20ancestral%20house%20in%20Kucha%20Chelan%20may%20well%20have%20appeared%20primitive%20to%20young%20Aruna%2C%20brought%20up%20with%20more%20modern%20Western%20conveniences.%20On%20returning%20from%20England%20Asaf%20himself%20had%20had%20difficulties%20readjusting%20to%20living%20there.%20How%20would%20Aruna%2C%20with%20her%20convent%20school%20education%20and%20anglicized%20Bengali%20family%20background%2C%20cope%20with%20daily%20life%20deep%20in%20the%20by-lanes%20of%20the%20old%20city%3F%20She%20later%20recollected%3A%20%E2%80%98When%20I%20first%20came%20to%20live%20in%20Delhi%20after%20my%20marriage%20in%20September%201928%2C%20I%20belonged%20to%20an%20entirely%20different%20hybrid%20Anglo%20Indianized%20background.%20There%20I%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20fit%20into%20a%20Muslim%20Indian%20way%20of%20living%2C%20hoary%20with%20customary%20manners%20and%20traditions.%E2%80%99%20She%20is%20described%20as%20being%20%E2%80%98shaken%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98kitchen%20bound%20domesticity%20and%20seclusion%20of%20women%E2%80%99%20and%20believed%20to%20have%20said%20later%2C%20only%20half%20seriously%20perhaps%2C%20that%20had%20she%20known%20what%20life%20in%20a%20typical%20Muslim%20home%20was%20like%2C%20she%20would%20not%20have%20married%20Asaf%20Ali!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20344px)%2085vw%2C%20344px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21120132%2F71ys9JOmTVL._SY522_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22344%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21120132%2F71ys9JOmTVL._SY522_.jpg%20344w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21120132%2F71ys9JOmTVL._SY522_-198x300.jpg%20198w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-702581%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22522%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ET.C.A.%20Raghavan%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3ECircles%20of%20Freedom%3A%20Friendship%2C%20Love%20and%20Loyalty%20in%20The%20Indian%20National%20Struggle%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EJuggernaut%2C%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nineteen-year-old%20showed%20a%20lot%20of%20determination%20and%20staying%20power.%20She%20did%20not%20accept%20Asaf%20%E2%80%99s%20offer%20that%20they%20move%20out%20of%20Kucha%20Chelan%20to%20a%20modern%20flat%20as%20that%20would%20have%20left%20his%20mother%20bereft.%20%E2%80%98Special%20toilet%20arrangements%20were%20made%20for%20her%2C%20and%20it%20was%20accepted%20that%20the%20customary%20observance%20of%20seclusion%20would%20not%20apply%20in%20her%20case.%E2%80%99%20Aruna%20settled%20down%20in%20the%20old%20haveli%20%E2%80%93%20amidst%20%E2%80%98open%20drains%20running%20alongside%20the%20congested%20streets%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20initially%20managing%20as%20well%20as%20she%20could%20and%20then%20settling%20down%20to%20become%20a%20member%20of%20its%20community.%20But%20it%20was%20also%20apparent%20to%20her%20that%20the%20twenty-year%20age%20difference%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20her%20own%20youth%20meant%20that%20the%20transition%20to%20being%20the%20wife%20of%20a%20public%20figure%20would%20not%20be%20an%20easy%20one.%20In%20her%20recollection%2C%20in%20the%20early%20days%20after%20the%20marriage%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20was%20almost%20in%20purdah%20.%20.%20.%20not%20that%20my%20husband%20believed%20in%20it%2C%20but%20I%20just%20felt%20shy.%20I%20felt%2C%20oh%2C%20I%20would%20be%20abused%2C%20rather%20I%20seemed%20to%20have%20put%20my%20foot%20into%20something%20for%20which%20I%20was%20not%20prepared.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20her%20diffidence%20and%20awkwardness%20when%2C%20a%20little%20after%20the%20wedding%2C%20the%20couple%20was%20invited%20to%20a%20dinner%20party%20by%20a%20senior%20civil%20servant%2C%20Brijlal%20Nehru%2C%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20New%20Delhi%20(called%20%E2%80%98Lutyens%20Delhi%E2%80%99%20today).%20Brijlal%20was%20a%20nephew%20of%20Motilal%20Nehru%3B%20the%20occasion%20was%20that%20Motilal%20was%20in%20town%20and%20Jawaharlal%20would%20also%20be%20joining%20them%20for%20dinner.%20Brijlal%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Rameshwari%20Nehru%20was%20active%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20issues%20and%20later%20would%20also%20be%20active%20in%20Gandhian%20efforts%20to%20work%20with%20Dalits.%20Despite%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20career%20in%20the%20civil%20service%2C%20she%20was%20drawn%20to%20nationalism%20and%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%201940s%20during%20the%20Quit%20India%20movement.%20Towards%20the%20end%20of%20her%20life%20Rameshwari%20would%20be%20head%20of%20the%20Harijan%20Sevak%20Sangh%2C%20one%20of%20the%20important%20Congress%20organizations.%20All%20this%20was%20in%20the%20future%2C%20however%3B%20in%20the%20winter%20of%201928%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20dinner%20party%2C%20Brijlal%20Nehru%20had%20recently%20been%20posted%20to%20the%20capital%20city%20and%20Rameshwari%20had%20thrown%20herself%20into%20social%20work%20and%20established%20the%20Delhi%20Women%E2%80%99s%20League%20to%20this%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsaf%20was%20acquainted%20with%20Motilal%20because%20both%20were%20practising%20lawyers%20and%20their%20common%20involvement%20in%20the%20Congress%20had%20drawn%20them%20closer%20together.%20As%20we%20had%20seen%2C%20Motilal%20was%20a%20supporter%20of%20Asaf%20%E2%80%99s%20failed%20bid%20to%20get%20elected%20to%20the%20Central%20Legislative%20Assembly%20and%20had%20taken%20his%20defeat%20as%20a%20political%20setback%20for%20himself.%20Motilal%20was%20a%20leading%20%E2%80%98Swarajist%E2%80%99%20and%20Asaf%20was%20part%20of%20the%20large%20group%20that%20supported%20his%20view%20that%20the%20Congress%20should%20supplement%20its%20agitational%20and%20protest%20activity%20with%20participation%20in%20the%20legislative%20bodies%20set%20up%20by%20the%20colonial%20state%20even%20if%20they%20had%20only%20limited%20mandates.%20That%20Asaf%20would%20be%20invited%20for%20a%20private%20dinner%20for%20Motilal%20was%20therefore%20not%20surprising.%20Yet%20the%20evening%20in%20Brijlal%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20bungalow%20had%2C%20in%20Aruna%E2%80%99s%20memory%2C%20a%20subtext%3A%20%E2%80%98the%20establishment%20Nehru%E2%80%99%20had%20invited%20the%20Asaf%20Alis%20because%20their%20%E2%80%98seditious%20clansmen%20from%20Allahabad%20were%20visiting%E2%80%99.%20Motilal%20and%20Jawaharlal%20were%20obviously%20the%20%E2%80%98seditious%20clansmen%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20communal%20situation%20in%20Delhi%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20was%2C%20especially%20with%20Asaf%20present%2C%20an%20obvious%20conversation%20point.%20But%20there%20would%20have%20been%20others.%20Much%2C%20if%20not%20all%2C%20of%20this%20was%20way%20beyond%20Aruna%3B%20she%20recollected%20later%3A%20%E2%80%98I%20felt%20lost%20in%20what%20struck%20me%20as%20a%20sombre%20gathering%20of%20elderly%20persons%20talking%20about%20the%20problems%20of%20the%20day%20of%20which%20I%20was%20utterly%20ignorant.%E2%80%99%20Jawaharlal%20arrived%20late%2C%20coming%20straight%20from%20a%20speaking%20tour%20in%20the%20Punjab%20%E2%80%98all%20covered%20in%20dust%E2%80%99%20and%20Aruna%20was%20%E2%80%98dazzled%20by%20the%20first%2C%20close%20look%20of%20him%E2%80%99.%20She%20also%20recalled%20that%20%E2%80%98he%20looked%20me%20up%20and%20down%20with%20amused%20curiosity%E2%80%99%3B%20she%20%E2%80%98was%20wearing%20a%20silk%20sari%20and%20some%20jewellry%20%5Bsic%5D%20%E2%80%93%20a%20dolled%20up%20slip%20of%20a%20girl%20destined%20to%20decorate%20drawing%20rooms%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ET.C.A.%20Raghavan%20is%20a%20former%20Indian%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20Pakistan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711009838000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21120337%2FAruna-Asaf-Ali.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fhow-aruna-and-asaf-ali-found-the-balance-in-the