rUxbfqkDatmHy12e%252FzBiU51zPFZI5qMtjV1qgjFjVCLfCrR65PIpVS5CsMV%252FGVTR3%252B6uhrbgZprhECh1UHCSv%252B1yJkuMeCkTzY9fhBvw%253D%253D%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20EC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20had%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthough%20the%20letters%20were%20sent%20out%20before%20MCC%20%5BModel%20Code%20of%20Conduct%5D%20period%2C%20but%20due%20to%20system%20architecture%20and%20network%20limitations%20it%20is%20possible%20that%20some%20letters%20have%20a%20delayed%20delivery%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Commission%20has%20received%20complaints%20from%20various%20quarters%20that%20such%20messages%20are%20still%20being%20delivered%20on%20citizens%E2%80%99%20phones.%20Since%20the%20MCC%20is%20now%20in%20force%2C%20you%20are%20hereby%20directed%20to%20ensure%20forthwith%20that%20no%20further%20delivery%20of%20%E2%80%98WhatsApp%20messages%E2%80%99%20take%20place%20during%20MCC%20period.%20A%20compliance%20report%20in%20this%20regard%20may%20be%20sent%20immediately%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20EC%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC%20notice%20does%20not%20say%20that%20any%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20on%20the%20messages%20already%20sent%20after%20the%20MCC%20was%20already%20in%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fprima-facie-mcc-violation-chandigarh-authorities-refer-modis-mass-whatsapp-message-to-ec%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20Chandigarh%20election%20authorities%20had%20said%20that%20the%20WhatsApp%20messages%2C%20being%20send%20in%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20were%20a%20%E2%80%9Cprima%20facie%20violation%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20MCC%2C%20and%20referred%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20EC%20given%20its%20all-India%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20relates%20to%20the%20circulation%20of%20bulk%20messages%20to%20millions%20of%20Indians%20on%20WhatsApp%20from%20%E2%80%98Viksit%20Bharat%20Sampark%E2%80%99%2C%20with%20a%20letter%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20attached.%20The%20Viksit%20Bharat%20Sampark%20account%20had%20the%20registered%20office%20address%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%2C%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELargely%20highlighting%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20in%20past%20ten%20years%2C%20Modi%20in%20the%20letter%20stated%20that%20transformation%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20people%20was%20the%20biggest%20achievement%20of%20his%20government.%20He%20then%20sought%20people%E2%80%99s%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711008890000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19115117%2FScreenshot-2024-03-19-at-8.22.50-AM-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fec-tells-it-ministry-to-immediately-stop-sending-viksit-bharat-messages-with-modis-letter%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ministry%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20messages%20were%20meant%20to%20go%20out%20before%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20was%20in%20place%2C%20but%20were%20delivered%20late%20because%20of%20a%20system%20error.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fec-tells-it-ministry-to-immediately-stop-sending-viksit-bharat-messages-with-modis-letter%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22''4.5%20Hours%20Of%20Sleep''%3A%20X%20User%20Shares%20IIT-JEE%20Aspirant's%20Rigorous%20Schedule%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0IIT%20JEE%20(Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20%E2%80%93%20Joint%20Entrance%20Exam)%20and%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%20exam%20are%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20most%20prestigious%20exams%20in%20India%20and%20are%20attempted%20by%20lakhs%20of%20students%20across%20the%20country%20every%20year.%20The%20exams%20deemed%20to%20be%20the%20toughest%20in%20the%20country%20demand%20strategic%20planning%2C%20focused%20dedication%2C%20and%20a%20disciplined%20approach.%20Recently%2C%20a%20user%20on%20X%20shared%20the%20rigid%20schedule%20of%20a%20friend%20preparing%20for%20the%20JEE%20(Joint%20Entrance%20Examination)%2C%20underscoring%20the%20significance%20of%20time%20management.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20user%20who%20goes%20by%20the%20name%20Mr.%20Rc%20on%20X%20and%20identifies%20himself%20as%20a%2016-year-old%2C%20shared%20a%20handwritten%20timetable%20of%20his%2017-year-old%20friend.%20''Schedule%20of%20a%20close%20friend%20who%20is%20preparing%20for%20JEE%2C''%20the%20caption%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20screenshot%20of%20the%20timetable%20outlined%20his%20daily%20activities%2C%20his%20sleep%20schedule%20and%20the%20time%20allocated%20to%20studies.%20The%20young%20aspirant%20gets%20up%20at%204%3A30%20am%20every%20day%2C%C2%A0after%20sleeping%20at%20midnight%2C%20getting%20just%204.5%20hours%20of%20sleep.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20day%20goes%20into%20revising%20old%20chapters%2C%20attending%20class%2C%20and%20completing%20class%20work%20and%20notes%20with%20hardly%20any%20time%20for%20leisure%20or%20other%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20picture%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F99hd5c8o_iit-jee-aspirant-schedule_625x300_21_March_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20motivate%20himself%2C%20the%20student%20also%20wrote%20an%20inspirational%20quote%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20schedule%20that%20read%2C%20''Never%20will%20you%20have%20this%20day%20again.%20So%20make%20it%20count.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20user%20who%20shared%20the%20post%20further%20said%20that%20his%20friend%20follows%20the%20timetable%20very%20precisely%20and%20is%20''filled%20with%20determination%20to%20bring%20his%20family%20out%20of%20poverty.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20his%20post%2C%20one%20user%20said%2C%20''Too%20hectic..no%20time%20for%20physical%20activity.''%20Another%20commented%2C%20''This%20looks%20good%2C%20especially%20those%20power-naps.%20Would%20request%20to%20begin%20the%20day%20with%20meditation%2Frunning%20and%20add%20any%20sports%20for%2030%20minutes%20later%20in%20the%20day.%20All%20the%20best.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20said%2C%20''Medical%20evidence%20shows%20that%20sleeping%20less%20than%207-8%20hours%20in%20teenage%20years%20leads%20to%20poor%20memory%2C%20lower%20learning%2C%20and%20atrophied%20problem-solving%20skills%20-%20everything%20teens%20need.%20Your%20friend%20should%20sleep%20more!''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fourth%20added%2C%20''that's%20some%20insane%20discipline%20if%20he%20does%20it%20consistently.%20My%20routine%20for%20NEET%20and%20JEE%20was%20very%20indisciplined%20and%20vague.%20Altho%20I%20had%20a%20decent%20success%2C%20but%20still%20I%20wish%20I%20was%20somewhat%20disciplined%20during%20prep%20time.%20may%20be%20it%20would%20have%20reduced%20some%20unnecessary%20stress.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20exam%20is%20divided%20into%20two%20levels%3A%20JEE%20Mains%20and%20JEE%20Advanced.%20Candidates%20have%20to%20first%20qualify%20for%20JEE%20Mains%20to%20appear%20for%20the%20advanced%20level%20of%20the%20entrance%20exam%20(JEE%20Advanced).%20The%20exam%20is%20held%20twice%20a%20year%20in%20office%20mode.%20The%20first%20exam%20is%20held%20in%20January%20and%20the%20second%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711007220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Feh0cjbo_iitjee-aspirants-schedule_625x300_21_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2F4-5-hours-of-sleep-x-user-shares-iit-jee-aspirants-rigid-daily-schedule-5281307%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20user%20on%20X%20shared%20the%20rigid%20schedule%20of%20a%20friend%20preparing%20for%20the%20JEE%20(Joint%20Entrance%20Examination).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2F4-5-hours-of-sleep-x-user-shares-iit-jee-aspirants-rigid-daily-schedule-5281307%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2F4-5-hours-of-sleep-x-user-shares-iit-jee-aspirants-rigid-daily-schedule-5281307%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2F4-5-hours-of-sleep-x-user-shares-iit-jee-aspirants-rigid-daily-schedule-5281307%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Parties%20Got%20Rs%207%2C726%20Cr%20in%20Non-Electoral%20Bond%20Funds%20Between%202013-23%2C%20Nearly%2065%25%20Went%20to%20the%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F08223208%2Frupee-g9dbf1131e_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Political%20parties%20received%20Rs%207%2C726%20crore%20in%20non-electoral%20bond%20donations%20between%202013-2023%20according%20to%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20data%2C%20%3Cem%3EBusinessline%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fdata-stories%2Fdata-focus%2Fparties-garnered-7726-crore-in-transparent-donations-between-2013-23%2Farticle67972138.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20Rs%207%2C726%20crore%2C%20the%20BJP%20received%20nearly%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20or%2064.7%25%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Congress%20(10.7%25)%2C%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(3.3%25)%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(3.1%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fdata-stories%2Fdata-focus%2Fparties-garnered-7726-crore-in-transparent-donations-between-2013-23%2Farticle67972138.ece%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20the%20total%20donation%20was%20made%20through%20transparent%20means%20of%20political%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20in%202018%2C%20donations%20to%20political%20parties%20that%20exceeded%20Rs%2020%2C000%20had%20to%20be%20declared%20under%20the%20political%20finance%20laws%20implemented%20in%202003%20by%20the%20Bharaitya%20Janata%20Party-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20donations%2C%20incentivised%20by%20100%25%20tax%20deductibility%2C%20saw%20a%20notable%20increase%20over%20the%20years%2C%20reaching%20Rs%201%2C247%20crore%20in%20FY20%20from%20Rs%20309%20crore%20in%20FY14.%20However%2C%20donations%20witnessed%20a%20slight%20decline%20to%20Rs%201%2C101%20crore%20in%20FY23%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECorporate%20donations%20also%20play%20a%20significant%20role%2C%20with%20entities%20such%20as%20Prudent%20Electoral%20Trust%20(PET)%20emerging%20as%20leading%20contributors.%20In%20FY23%2C%20PET%20contributed%20Rs%20256%20crore%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20Rs%2090%20crore%20to%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS).%20Additionally%2C%20M%2FS%20MKJ%20Enterprises%20Limited%20disbursed%20Rs%2045%20crore%20to%20the%20INC%2C%20while%20B.G.%20Shirke%20Construction%20Technology%20PVT%20Limited%20donated%20%E2%82%B935%20crore%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20paper%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fdata-stories%2Fdata-focus%2Fparties-garnered-7726-crore-in-transparent-donations-between-2013-23%2Farticle67972138.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20Verma%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%2C%20explained%20the%20transition%20from%20transparent%20to%20opaque%20political%20donations%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CParty%20politics%20in%20India%20has%20become%20increasingly%20competitive%20over%20the%20years%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20rise%20in%20party%20expenditures%20for%20elections.%20To%20meet%20these%20growing%20expenses%2C%20parties%20often%20rely%20on%20resources%20generated%20from%20the%20corporate%20sector.%20This%20dynamic%20has%20resulted%20in%20the%20development%20of%20opaque%20funding%20mechanisms.%20Regardless%20of%20which%20political%20party%20is%20in%20power%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20utilize%20funding%20mechanisms%20to%20their%20advantage%2C%E2%80%9D%20Verma%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fdata-stories%2Fdata-focus%2Fparties-garnered-7726-crore-in-transparent-donations-between-2013-23%2Farticle67972138.ece%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Eswaran%20Sridharan%20and%20Milan%20Vaishnav%2C%20authors%20of%20%3Cem%3ECosts%20of%20Democracy%3A%20Political%20Finance%20in%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20nearly%2075%25%20of%20money%20received%20by%20the%20six%20national%20parties%20comes%20through%20anonymous%20donations%20that%20are%20below%20the%20Rs%2020%2C000%20limit%2C%20the%20report%20highlighted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711007110000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F08223208%2Frupee-g9dbf1131e_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparties-got-rs-rs-7726-cr-in-non-electoral-bond-funds-between-2013-23-nearly-65-went-to-the-bjp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Of%20the%20Rs%207%2C726%20crore%2C%20the%20BJP%20received%20nearly%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20or%2064.7%25%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Congress%20(10.7%25)%2C%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(3.3%25)%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(3.1%25).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparties-got-rs-rs-7726-cr-in-non-electoral-bond-funds-between-2013-23-nearly-65-went-to-the-bjp%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Rapper%20Badshah%20on%20New%20Album%20%E2%80%98Ek%20Tha%20Raja%2C%E2%80%99%20Working%20With%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20Arijit%20Singh%3A%20%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99m%20Like%20This%20Cousin%20Who%20Starts%20the%20Party%E2%80%99%20