%80%9CWe%20had%20always%20been%20very%20environmentally%20conscious%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gaurang%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20consciousness%20evolved%20into%20a%20desire%20to%20take%20macro-level%20actions%20when%20the%20duo%20began%20volunteering%20at%20a%20Mumbai-based%20NGO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20met%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20NGO%2C%20Julius%2C%20who%20left%20us%20inspired%20by%20the%20work%20he%20was%20doing%2C%20and%20soon%20we%20became%20friends.%20He%20was%20involved%20in%20conservation%20efforts%20of%20the%20tribal%20parts%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gaurang%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20visited%20rural%20areas%20to%20meet%20the%20tribals%20striving%20to%20become%20more%20eco-conscious%20and%20even%20transition%20to%20organic%20farming%2C%20we%20discovered%20they%20faced%20challenges%20with%20the%20supply%20chain%20and%20reaching%20the%20right%20consumers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4VYFDTIiBJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4VYFDTIiBJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4VYFDTIiBJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Monks%20Bouffe%20(%40monksbouffe)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20realisation%20sparked%20an%20idea%20in%20the%20brothers.%20They%20decided%20to%20transition%20to%20this%20sector%20and%20assist%20the%20tribal%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20thought%20we%20would%20have%20our%20own%20farm%20but%20decided%20against%20it%20as%20we%20felt%20that%20the%20community%20needed%20our%20help%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20brothers%20were%20very%20sure%20of%20their%20idea%2C%20their%20friends%20and%20family%20were%20a%20little%20sceptical.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20something%20which%20was%20not%20the%20plan%20of%20our%20family%20for%20us.%20It%20became%20very%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20understand%20the%20need%20for%20such%20a%20shift.%20Additionally%2C%20back%20when%20we%20started%20in%202016%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20organic%20farming%2C%20the%20conservation%20of%20native%20trees%20was%20not%20very%20popular%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20had%20an%20urge%20to%20go%20for%20it%20anyway.%20In%202016%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20start%20%E2%80%98Monk%20Bouffe%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20bringing%20tribal%20produce%20to%20the%20right%20buyers%2C%20and%20have%20never%20looked%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENatural%2C%20organic%20and%20edible%20Holi%20colours%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20one%20of%20their%20conservation%20efforts%20across%20the%20tribal%20areas%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chattisgarh%2C%20the%20duo%20encountered%20people%20from%20the%20Bhil%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20community%2C%20based%20on%20the