C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThis%20year%2C%20out%20of%2035%20applicants%2C%2010%20were%20awarded%20the%20fellowship%20following%20thorough%20rounds%20of%20interviews%20and%20pitches.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReviving%20traditions%20and%20unveiling%20wisdom%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevelopment%2C%20which%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20decline%20in%20tribal%20populations%2C%20is%20now%20being%20used%20to%20preserve%20culture.%20Amabel%20and%20Banwang%20are%20using%20digital%20media%20to%20document%20their%20language%20and%20lullabies.%20A%20simple%20act%20of%20writing%20and%20recording%20is%20doing%20wonders%20for%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2035%20applications%2C%2010%20received%20the%20fellowship%20after%20rigorous%20rounds%20of%20interviews%20and%20pitches%20this%20year.%20And%20in%20between%20the%20process%2C%20all%20the%20applicants%20went%20through%20skill%20upgradation%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20applicants%20have%20great%20ideas%20but%20are%20not%20savvy%20enough%20to%20write%20a%20proposal%20or%20give%20a%20presentation.%20When%20we%20think%20of%20diversity%2C%20we%20often%20forget%20about%20the%20tribals.%20We%20think%20they%20are%20primitive%20and%20live%20in%20jungles.%20But%20when%20you%20read%20the%20proposals%2C%20you%20learn%20their%20diverse%20wisdom%2C%20culture%20and%20history.%20Through%20this%20fellowship%2C%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20preserve%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Oinam%20Doren%2C%20a%20jury%20member%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20Samvaad%20fellows%202023%20include%20%E2%80%94%20Saka%20Mashangva%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344734%2Ftata-samvaad-jamshedpur-sumanti-devi-artisan-preserves-oraon-art-mud-natural-finger-painting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efolk%20artist%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20